name: Tiger 3
description: Tiger (Salman Khan) is informed about a new military group that is planning something beyond all imagination, headed by a deeply motivated Aatish Rehman (Emraan Hashmi), who has a history of his own with Tiger and a personal vendetta to settle. Tiger & Zoya (Katrina Kaif), along with their compatriots, must overcome some arms dealers, assassins and the immensely calculative Aatish.

name: Devil - The British Secret Agent
description: Devil, a British officer, is assigned the task of unravelling the mystery behind the murder of a Zamindar’s daughter. As he delves into the details of the case, he encounters a conspiracy much bigger and deeper. Can devil solve the case and alter the course of history?

name: Calling Sahasra
description: Cyber expert Ajay joins new job but past tragedy motivates avenging crimes on women using RESQ app anonymously. Mass calls draw him into murder case amidst rescuing women.

name: Antony
description: When Anna enters the life of a criminal Antony, his life embarks on a transformation. As he starts enjoying his new life, his enemies return seeking revenge.

name: Mast Mein Rehne Ka
description: A man chooses an old widower's home for his first robbery, kicking off a set of events that have them both look at life in a new way and with new companions in the starkness of the city of Mumbai.

name: Dry Day
description: When his wife makes a vow to abort their baby due to his alcoholism, Gannu, the biggest loafer of Jagodhar sets out on a protest to ban alcohol in his town all the while grappling with his own drinking habits!

name: Talk to Me
description: When a group of friends discover how to conjure spirits using an embalmed hand, they become hooked on the new thrill, until one of them goes too far and unleashes terrifying supernatural forces.

name: 80s Buildup
description: A youngster accepts his sister's challenge to make the girl who has come to his grandfather's funeral to fall in love with him before the last rites are done.

name: Mission: Impossible - Dead Reckoning Part One
description: Ethan Hunt (Tom Cruise) and his IMF team embark on their most dangerous mission yet: To track down a terrifying new weapon that threatens all of humanity before it falls into the hands of a mysterious, all-powerful enemy.

name: Kaathal - The Core
description: Kaathal The Core unveils the captivating narrative of Mathew Devassy and Omana a seemingly harmonious couple residing in the serine village of Teekoy in Kottayam District Kaathal The Core is a poignant exploration of the intricate dynamics of a marriage the pursuit of justice and the quest of personal fulfilment set against the backdrop of a closeknit community.

name: Zakir Khan: Mannpasand
description: In his hilarious new special, Zakir recounts stories of his childhood friendships with boys, adult relationships with girls, and the clashes that ensue between them on one fateful Goa trip. As he explains, there are times when you have to choose between the right thing to do and the fun thing to do. In Mannpasand, Zakir firmly chooses fun.

name: Role Play
description: Emma (Kaley Cuoco) and Dave (David Oyelowo) spice up their wedding anniversary with a night of role-play in New York City. But things turn perilous when Emma's secret life as an international assassin, unknown to Dave, is exposed by Bob (Bill Nighy), jeopardizing her family. Emma must rely on her lethal skills and determination to protect her family at all costs.

name: Bhagavanth Kesari (I Don't Care)
description: Bhagavanth Kesari (Balakrishna) wishes Vijaya Lakshmi, aka Viji (Sreeleela), to become strong and brave. He wants her to join the Indian Army for a solid reason. However, Viji has no interest in it. Meanwhile, Rahul Sanghvi (Arjun Rampal) pursues her for a compelling reason. What motivates his pursuit of Viji? What is the connection between Bhagavanth Kesari and Viji? Did Viji join the Army?

name: FOE
description: Hen (Saoirse Ronan) & Junior’s (Paul Mescal) life is thrown into turmoil when a stranger shows up at their door with a startling proposal. Will they risk their relationship & personal identity for a chance to survive in a new world? With mesmerizing imagery and persistent questions about the nature of humanity (and artificial humanity), Foe brings the not-too-distant future to luminous life.

name: Chatrapathi - For The People
description: Separated from his family during a conflict, a refugee embarks on a mission to reunite with his adopted family. However, he faces several challenges after his foster brother conspires against him.

name: My Name Is Shruthi
description: It is an intriguing thriller based on Organ Mafia. My Name Is Shruthi stands apart as it deals with skin mafia, which is first of its kind movie which gives audience a new experience with a gripping thriller.

name: Tiger Nageswara Rao
description: A story about a deadly thief who challenges to rob PM house. IB officer, Rajput, who investigates about him, comes to know that he's more than an thief. While he tries to stop the robbery, the story unfolds in different path

name: Reacher - Season 2
description: When members of Reacher’s old military unit start turning up dead, Reacher has just one thing on his mind—revenge.

name: Phoenix
description: Phoenix is a horror film that has got a love story equally embedded within. The story takes off when the protagonist John and his family relocate to a faraway island village with the hopes of rebuilding their lives. But destiny has other plans for them as a series of horrifying events begin to unfold.

name: Wedding.con
description: Wedding.con is a true crime documentary series about five women who seek to fulfill a universal dream - Marriage. However, in their search for the perfect life-partner, they end up getting exploited financially and emotionally by conmen with fake identities, posing as suitable grooms on popular online platforms.

name: Tagarupalya
description: Pandappa from remote village of Mandya, vows to perform pooja if he finds a suitable match for his daughter. When he fixes her marriage to a software engineer from Bengaluru, he invites the whole village for the same.

name: Garudan
description: When Nishanth (Biju Menon), a college lecturer, and DCP Harish Madhav (Suresh Gopi), a straightforward police officer, become involved in a crime, one of them must battle for justice and the other for his integrity. Both men must outwit one another in a network of deceit and mental tricks.

name: Flames - Season 4
description: Centered around 12th-grade students facing impending board exams, Rajat-Ishita and Pandu-Anusha navigates the delicate balance between love and studies. As Kaushal sir teaches in a different institute, doubts arise about his commitment to excellence. Rajat and Ishita embark on a journey, exploring the intersections of career and love and questions of a long distance relationship.

name: Bhagavanth Kesari (Hindi)
description: Nelakonda Bhagavanth Kesari is adamant about getting even with a powerful businessman who cost him money. He is prepared to square off against the formidable foe and resolve their issues amicably.

name: Pippa
description: PIPPA tells the story of Captain Balram Singh Mehta of India’s 45 Cavalry regiment who, along with his siblings, fought on the eastern front during the Indo-Pakistani war of 1971. Named after the Russian amphibious war tank “PT-76”, which floats on water like an empty ‘pippa’ (tin) of ghee, the film traces Mehta's coming-of-age as he steps up to prove himself in a war to liberate Bangladesh.

name: Welcome 2 Karachi
description: Welcome 2 Karachi Is A Bollywood Action Hindi War Movie, Directed By Ashish R Mohan, Starring Arshad Warsi And Jackky Bhagnani In The Lead Roles. Two Friends Land Up In Karachi Without Their Passports After They Are Kidnapped During Their Boat Trip. When They Realise The Severity Of Being Kidnapped By The Taliban, They Look For Ways To Escape.

name: Swathi Mutthina Male Haniye
description: A hospice counsellor, Prerana, finds a new meaning in her life when she befriends Aniketh, a terminally ill patient. Their bond challenges the conventional notions of love, life and humanity.

name: Woh 3 Din
description: Woh 3 Din is a Hindi movie released on 30 Sep, 2022. The movie is directed by Raaj Aashoo and featured Sanjay Mishra, Rajesh Sharma, Chandan Roy Sanyal, and Rakesh Srivastava as lead characters. Other popular actors who were roped in for Woh 3 Din are Purva Parag and Payel Mukherjee.

name: Satyaprem Ki Katha
description: Sattu is a good hearted but good for nothing LLB fail guy who dreams of marrying the IT girl of Ahmedabad Katha, a girl way out of his league. However fate has other plans and Katha and he end up getting married, much to Katha’s dismay. From here on starts Sattu’s tryst to make his wife fall in love with him and how while doing so, he ends up discovering himself and proves to be a worthy husband!

name: Viswasam (HINDI)
description: Jayveera, a chieftain, gets separated from his wife, Ranjana Rai, after their daughter, Swetha, gets injured during a fight. Years later, he tries to protect Swetha without revealing his identity.

name: Jack Reacher
description: Investigator Jack Reacher leaps off the pages of Lee Child’s novel and onto the big screen in this thriller. When a horrible crime is committed, all evidence points to the suspect in custody who offers up a single note in defense: “Get Jack Reacher!”

name: Partner
description: Best friends who steal for a living. When they try to steal from a scientist, One of them falls trap to one of his scientific experiments, transforming him into a woman.

name: Hypnotic
description: Austin detective Danny Rourke investigates a mystery involving his missing daughter and a secret government program that finds himself spiralling down a rabbit hole of a series of reality-bending crimes.

name: The Trial
description: Roopa (Spandana Palli), a Hyderabad policewoman, faces tragedy on her anniversary as her husband, Ajay (Yug Ram), falls to his death. After moving on, accusations of murder resurface from Ajay's family, triggering an investigation led by Rajeev (Vamsi Kotu). Unveiling shocking revelations, the movie delves into the truth behind the mysterious demise, questioning Roopa's innocence

name: Adipurush
description: Raghav, Ayodhya’s exiled prince, embarks on a quest to rescue his wife Janaki with the help of a monkey army, from the clutches of Lanka’s ten-headed demon king Raavan.

name: Consecration
description: After the alleged suicide of her priest brother, Grace travels to the remote Scottish convent. As she explores the wild cliffs and windswept beaches nearby, she uncovers what really happened with the help of Vatican priest, not only the murder but a disturbing truth about her own past which brings long-buried trauma to the surface.

name: Tantiram
description: Balachandran avoided interaction with women and preferred to be alone due to a bad past with his mother. Everything changes when he marries a beautiful girl named Alagini who changes him into a jovial and loving person. Things turn upside down when The Jinn, a supernatural entity enters in Balachandran life.

name: Ala Ninnu Cheri
description: Wealthy village belle Divya (Payal) falls in love with Ganesh (Dinesh Tej), dreaming of becoming a film director. When her single mother attempts to arrange her marriage, Divya contemplates eloping with Ganesh. However, he hesitates due to his ambition.  The plot unfolds when Ganesh, charmed by the beautiful Anu (Hebah Patel), finds himself entangled in a love story that takes unexpected turns.

name: LGM (let's get married)
description: The life of a young man takes an unexpected turn when his girlfriend asks him to join her on a trip with her mother before they consider getting married to assess their compatibility. This journey becomes a humorous and heart-warming adventure, challenging beliefs about love, family, and the true essence of compatibility.

name: B.A. Pass
description: Orphaned and at loose ends, a young boy falls into the seductive orbit of a married woman, who leads him even deeper into a world of sex and betrayal.

name: Sniper: The White Raven
description: Based on true events Mykola is an eccentric Ukrainian pacifist who wants to be useful to humanity. When Russia-Ukraine War begins in eastern Ukraine's region of Donbas in 2014, Mykola's naive world is collapsing as Russian soldiers kill his pregnant wife. With his peaceful life over and nothing left to live for, Mykola joins the Ukrainian Army and, after a short training, becomes a sniper.

name: B.A. Pass 2
description: A young woman eager to avoid an arranged marriage moves to Mumbai, where she learns hard truths about show business, life and love.

name: Kida
description: The story revolves around three characters - a grandfather, his grandson and his pet goat and a butcher. They are forced to take hard decisions to fulfill their dreams by the dawn of Diwali.

name: Born to Fly
description: Two American F-35 Lightning II fighters enter Chinese airspace and cause havoc near the coast. Flying at supersonic speeds, the F-35s create sonic booms that damage an oil refinery and fishing boats. Box office smash hit & multiple award winner Born to Fly comes to life with special operations team headed by elite pilots who face death and challenge the limits of the sky and themselves.

name: Sugar Factory
description: Arya and Adithi Bopanna meets up in a pub, Where they pretend in a love relationship among their friends due to a challenge.

name: Rahasya
description: Rahasya Is An Award Winning Bollywood Murder Mystery Hindi Movie, Directed By Manish Gupta, Starring Kay Kay Menon, Tisca Chopra, Ashish Vidyarthi, Mita Vashisht And Ashwini Kalsekar In The Lead Roles. When Dr Sachin Mahajan Is Accused Of Killing Ayesha His Own Daughter, All The Evidence Is Against Him. However CBI Officer Paraskar Starts A Fresh Investigation Which Leads Him To Disturbing Truths.

name: Two Moon Junction
description: A beautiful southern debutante is about to marry a man just as privileged as she. But when she locks eyes with a rough-hewn, sensual carnival worker, she is drawn into an erotically charged battle of wills that will change her life forever.

name: After
description: Tessa Young is a dedicated student, dutiful daughter and loyal girlfriend to her high school sweetheart. Entering her first semester of college, Tessa's guarded world opens up when she meets Hardin Scott, a mysterious and brooding rebel who makes her question all she thought she knew about herself and what she wants out of life.

name: Minus 31: The Nagpur Files
description: While investigating an important murder amidst the second wave of the pandemic, an impulsive cop uncovers the dark realities of the system and reconciles with her true self.

name: Spider-Man: Homecoming
description: Peter Parker tries to live his life as a high school student while fighting the Vulture.

name: Major Ajay Krishna
description: Ajay Krishnaact (Mahesh Babu) is an orphan and a soldier serving in Kashmir. Professor Bharathi (Vijayashanthi) is a righteous professor and single mother of three, with one son already lost during service. How Ajay steps up when she's in trouble forms the crux of the story.

name: Little Miss Rawther
description: In this quirky film, a tall guy Abhijit, known as AB (Shersha Sheriff), and the a short woman , Naina Rawther (Gauri G Kishan), form an engaging opposites-attract couple. Abhijit exudes a slacker-stoner vibe, while Naina is characterized by her obsession with cleanliness and responsibility. A humorous quirk is their height difference, with Naina being short (4 feet) and Abhijit tall (6 feet).

name: Vyooham - Season 1
description: A newly appointed police officer is assigned to a hit and run case, where a pregnant couple lost their child. What seems like a simple open and shut case, turns out to be a complicated web involving several seemingly unconnected people. To solve the case, the officer has to hunt down a serial killer, a trained naxal, a suspended cop, and a terrorist organization, while facing his own painful past.

name: The Moon
description: In the near future, South Korea's first manned mission to the moon ends in a tragic disaster. Five years later, a second spaceflight leaves astronaut Sun-woo stranded in space. Facing another fatal catastrophe, the Naro Space Center turns to its former managing director Kim Jae-guk to help bring Sun-woo back home safely.

name: Marry My Husband - Season 1
description: Kang Ji-won, a terminally ill cancer patient, is killed by her husband and best friend after she witnesses them having an affair. She wakes up 10 years before the incident and decides to seek revenge with the help of Yu Ji-hyuk, a director at the company where she works. Now, she must reclaim her fate and eliminate the trash from her life.

name: Rules Ranjann
description: Kiran Abbavaram shines as Manoranjan, aka Rules Ranjann, a principled professional in Mumbai, silently falls in love with his schoolmate, Sana (Neha Shetty).  Ranjann returns to his village to confess his feelings, triggering a riotous reunion with friends Hyper Aadhi, Vennela Kishore, Sudarshan, and Viva Harsha. The second half is a laugh riot, culminating in a climactic finale.

name: Ek Tha Tiger
description: Tiger (Salman Khan) India’s top spy, is sent on a mission to Dublin to observe a scientist who is suspected of sharing information with the Pakistan defense. He meets the scientist’s part time home caretaker, Zoya (Katrina Kaif). As Tiger begins to get closer, he falls in love. What follows is a tumultuous journey that Tiger & Zoya embark upon, battling the dark world of intelligence and espionag

name: Amsterdam
description: Written and directed by acclaimed filmmaker David O. Russell comes an original crime epic about three close friends who find themselves at the center of one of the most shocking secret plots in American history. Based on facts that meet fiction, the film stars Christian Bale, Margot Robbie, John David Washington, with Rami Malek and Robert De Niro.

name: Section 375
description: A celebrated Bollywood director Rohan Khurana stands accused by a female member of his crew, Anjali Dangle of having raped her at his residence.

name: Raid
description: "A story about an ips officer prabhakaran, who takes an oath to eradicate wrongdoers in society. he faces many struggles and problems from the enemies. the plot and conclusion of this story is whether or not rowdyism has reduced in chennai."

name: Krishna Ghattam
description: Inspired by true events, "Krishna Ghattam" is a tale of morality and reform. Amidst turmoil, Prasad decides to stand tall. A casanova's pursuits meet his nemesis. A self-righteous boy is tested. Will there be reform? See the battle between wisdom and intelligence.

name: Silver and the Book of Dreams
description: When Liv moves to London, she meets the mysterious Henry and his group of friends, who pull her into the enthralling world of dream-travel. She and her newfound band of dream-wanderers conduct a ritual to make their biggest dream come true, but it demands the gravest sacrifice. Based on the bestseller by Kerstin Gier.

name: Legally Blonde
description: Elle has it all. She's president of her sorority, a natural blonde, and she dates the cutest fraternity boy on campus. There's just one thing stopping him from popping the question: Elle is too blonde. So, when he packs up for Harvard Law, Elle rallies all her resources and gets into Harvard, determined to win him back.

name: Pulikkuthi Pandi
description: A young man named Pulikkuthi Pandi fights injustice while trying to woo a beautiful woman. However, problems arise when he locks horns with a powerful individual.

800 is based on Muthiah Muralidaran's Life, the champion who set the record for taking 800 test wickets in Test Cricket. It is a moving portrayal of one of Cricket's most brilliant and divisive characters. A tale of unorthodoxy, ethnicity and pride. This is a tale of an oppressed Tamil, who championed Sri Lankan Cricket and went on to become one of the greatest Cricketer ever.

name: Dum Laga Ke Haisha
description: Prem is a shy music buff who runs a tape recording shop. Sandhya is about to carve a niche for herself as a teacher. Will a regular arranged marriage turn out to be a perfect mismatch? From overcoming his fear of the English language to dealing with an overbearing father, he discovers that his oversized wife, who he thought was a spanner in his spool, will actually lead him to something quite cool

name: Sultan
description: Sultan is a classic underdog tale about a wrestler's journey, looking for a comeback by defeating all odds staked up against him. But when he has nothing to lose and everything to gain in this fight for his life match, he must literally fight for his life. Sultan believes he’s got what it takes, but this time, it’s going to take everything he’s got.

name: Me Before You
description: A paralysed man develops a bond with his caregiver.

name: Dark Spell
description: Dark Spell is a Hindi dubbed version of a Russian blockbuster. Is a story about a woman named Zhenya who casts a spell called "Black Wedding" to bring her husband back. However, the spell turns his love into an obsession, and he becomes willing to even kill Zhenya so as not to give her to anyone. Even after his death, the spell does not stop, binding the two forever.

name: Somante Krithavu
description: The movie introduces us to Soman who takes charge as the village agriculture officer. His naturalist way of living often makes him a laughing stock in the village. He is often at loggerheads with the panchayat president for his forthright and honest personality.

name: Immature - Season 3
description: The school gang is back to school after a vacation. Dhruv has sworn off love and romance from his life. But either you follow love, or it follows you with Chaaya developing feelings for Dhruv. On the other hand, Dhruv is upset as there is rift between Kabir and Susu.

name: Sarkaaru Noukari
description: The story of a Government Employee who changed the ideology of the people which became a resolution.

name: Dhootha - Season 1
description: Journalist Sagar's life turns thrilling as he unravels dark secrets behind newspaper clippings predicting tragedies. He becomes a murder suspect, racing against time to clear his name and solve the enigma and faces dangerous twists. Suspense builds in this roller-coaster ride.

name: Thiruchitrambalam
description: A light-hearted tale about a food delivery guy Pazham, his breezy friendship with Shobana & a quirky bond with a quick-witted grandfather. Get swept in the fun n' frolic as they cheerfully navigate their messy lives.

name: Crimes Aaj Kal - Season 2
description: Crimes Aaj Kal is a show focused on the shocking incidents of crime which involve the youth of India, either as perpetrators or as the victims. As all the true-life inspired cases are woven together through a credible host, the show warns the viewers about the crimes happening in their very own neighborhood & how could they be safeguarded against them.

name: Tulip Fever
description: In 17th Century Amsterdam, an orphaned girl is forcibly married to a rich and powerful merchant that saves her from poverty. After her husband commissions a portrait, she begins a passionate affair with the painter. Seeking to escape the merchant’s ever-reaching grasp, the lovers risk everything and enter the tulip bulb market, with the hope that the right bulb will buy their freedom.

name: One Night Stand
description: A married man becomes infatuated with a woman who he has a one-night stand with after meeting her on a business trip. His obsession with his mistress threatens to uproot his marriage and everyday life.

name: Girls to Buy
description: Emi is a young ambitious girl who has been dreaming about a big world for years. Whenever an opportunity arises, she jumps into its modes without hesitation, becoming an exclusive escort. Soon it is she who, at the invitation of Arab sheikhs, begins to recruit Polish misses, celebrities, screen stars and models. However, this inaccessible, luxurious world will soon show its dark side.

name: Tathastu
description: Tathastu starts off with a recap of moments from Zakir's life. Starting from his early school days ,the performance is a ride where the audience gets a peek at the family he was born in, the characters he grew closest to and his young years bloated with aspirations of becoming an RJ. He goes onto share a few personal learnings on stage as he tries to make sense of his journey thus far.

name: Vaarasudu
description: Vijay, the prodigal son of business tycoon Rajendran agrees to take over the reins of the business, much to the chagrin of his brothers. But can Vijay prove himself to be a worthy varisu and also reunite his now-broken family? This movie is also available as Varisu (Tamil), Vamshajan (Malayalam) and Vaarasdara (Kannada)

name: Darbar (Hindi)
description: A police officer is on a chase to hunt down a dreaded gangster to fulfill his own secret agenda.

name: Little Big Soldier
description: An old soldier kidnaps a young General of an enemy state and takes him on a long journey to collect the reward.

name: Zindagi Na Milegi Dobara
description: The story about three old friends, Kabir (Abhay Deol), Arjun (Hrithik Roshan) and Imraan (Farhan Akhtar), reuniting after many years for a bachelor party trip before Kabir gets married. The trip changes their perception about life with many unforgettable experiences which include Laila (Katrina Kaif) and a lot of self-realisation. Watch the thrilling experience which teaches a lot about life.

name: Spark LIFE
description: Jay's love for Ananya leads to a deadly chain of events while Lekha's dreams collide with a stranger named Arya. As suicide killings grip the nation, a sinister force entwines their lives. Is Arya a friend or a foe?

name: Chak De India
description: "Kabir Khan (Shahrukh Khan), the ex Indian Captain has now come back as the Coach of the Women's National Hockey team. A rag-tag bunch of girls who’ve forgotten what it’s like to play for the love of the game. CHAK DE INDIA is the story of a coach's fight of making his team, Team India by overcoming their diverse backgrounds, by learning to use everything that life hurls on them as a secret weapon

name: Ambush
description: The thrilling true-story of a U.S Military suicide mission through miles of enemy, Vietcong infested tunnels. American forces are trapped on the edge of no-mans-land, facing danger amid a maze of tunnels as they pursue the Vietcong far below ground before a deadly secret can be exposed.

name: Dilwale Dulhania Le Jayenge
description: When Raj (Shahrukh Khan) & Simran (Kajol) first met on an inter-rail holiday in Europe, it wasn’t exactly Love at first sight but when Simran is taken back to India for an arranged marriage, things change. Encouraged by his father Dharamvir (Anupam Kher), Raj decides to fly down from London to not just win his Bride but her whole family and the blessings of her father Baldev Singh (Amrish Puri).

name: The Croods
description: A caveman (Nicolas Cage) and his family seek a new home when Mother Nature turns hostile.

name: 7:11 PM
description: The incident that takes place at 7:11 PM changes the fate of a town called Hamsala Deevi and a planet called Proxima-EV12. Ravi travels beyond imagination through time to stop a criminal mastermind, save his loved ones and his beloved town.

name: KisseBaaz
description: Its a revenge mystery that spins around an obscure situation where a helpless harsh gets into strange and regretful scenario planned by a shrewd narrator Chuttan Shukla, who could either be the cause or solution to a situation. This includes his quest to unravel the burning question Who is Ram Lal  ?

name: The Nun II Extended Preview
description: "The sequel to the worldwide smash hit The Nun follows Sister Irene as she once again comes face to face with the demonic force Valak—The Demon Nun."

name: The Lord of the Rings: The Fellowship of the Ring
description: In the first part of J.R.R. Tolkien's masterpiece, The Lord of the Rings, a young hobbit, Frodo Baggins, inherits a gold ring which holds the secret to the survival of the entire world.

name: Ae Dil Hai Mushkil
description: The trials and triumphs of unrequited love through the intertwining lives of Ayan, Alizeh and Saba.

name: Mark Antony
description: Mark, a skilled mechanic and the son of a former gangster, stumbles upon a time-travelling phone that can save his estranged mother from a grim fate, but he must navigate through dangerous consequences of altering the past while facing his own family's legacy.

name: Saat Uchakkey
description: Saat Uchakkey is a 2016 Indian Bollywood comedy film directed and written by Sanjeev Sharma, starring an ensemble cast of Manoj Bajpayee, Kay Kay Menon, Annu Kapoor, Vijay Raaz, Aditi Sharma, Jatin Sarna and Nitin Bhasin.

name: Every Day
description: Based on David Levithan’s novel, this charming romance tells the story of a 16-year-old girl (Angourie Rice) who falls in love with a spirit named A, a traveling soul who wakes each morning in a different body, living a different life...every day.

name: Legally Blonde 2: Red, White & Blonde
description: New lawyer Elle Woods heads to Washington, D.C., to bring her fight for animal rights to Congress in this sequel.

name: Transformers: Rise of the Beasts
description: Optimus Prime and the Autobots take on their biggest challenge yet. When a new threat capable of destroying the entire planet emerges, they must team up with a powerful faction of Transformers known as the Maximals to save Earth.

name: Death's Game
description: At the brink of going to hell, Yee-jae must cycle through twelve separate lives and twelve separate deaths in this reincarnation drama.

name: Veer-Zaara
description: Veer Pratap Singh (Shahrukh Khan) is a rescue pilot & rescues a stranded Zaara (Preity Zinta), a girl from Pakistan. His life is never the same again. 22 years later Saamia Siddiqui (Rani Mukerji), a Pakistani human rights lawyer, finds herself face to face with an ageing Veer Pratap Singh. He has languished in a Pakistan jail cell for 22 years. Her mission is to see to it that justice is served.

name: Ahimsa
description: A story of an youngster who follows the path of non-violence and finally revolts to a different path to get justice for his family!

name: Omerta
description: Ahmed Omar Saeed Sheikh, a terrorist of British origin, is willing to do whatever it takes to accomplish his vengeance-driven mission against the westerners in India.

name: Rajni
description: The story takes place in the city of Chennai. It revolves around the murder of Naveen's brother-in-law. Naveen attempts to track down the killer which leads to mysterious developments that unfolds.

name: Bholaa
description: Bholaa, an ex-convict, endeavours to meet his daughter for the first time after being released from prison. However his plans were interrupted by a well-orchestrated drug bust. His journey begins with an extraordinary encounter, and is littered with strange difficulties with death lurking around every turn. Things aren't as simple as they appear. Will he be able to meet his daughter?

name: A Weekend to Forget
description: The reunion of seven friends takes a deadly turn when old tensions resurface, leading to a murder. Trust is shattered, turning friends into enemies, and they must unravel the mystery behind the murder.

name: Jab We Met
description: The adversities of Aditya's business and love life bring him on the verge of committing suicide. One day, wandering aimlessly, he boards a train and bumps into Geet, a lively and talkative Punjabi Sikh girl, and just like that, without any inkling, Aditya's life changes forever.

name: Infinity
description: A series of murders happens in a City (Chennai), which is investigated by CBI Officer Evvi Ilavalavan (Natty Natraj). Will he find the answers for the question Who, How and Why of the crime, that too in time?

name: Neeyat
description: When a mysterious murder takes place at exiled billionaire Ashish Kapoor’s birthday party, the prime suspects are his close family and friends. ​As twists follow turns and devious motives are revealed, CBI officer Mira Rao must use all her skill to unravel a mystery where nothing is what it seems and everyone hides a secret or two.

name: Jack Reacher: Never Go Back
description: When Army Major Susan Turner is framed for treason, Jack Reacher discovers she's the target of a massive government conspiracy. Together, they will risk everything to take down a powerful organization that will stop at nothing to protect its secrets.

name: Mission: Impossible - Fallout
description: Ethan Hunt (Tom Cruise) chooses to save his team over completing a mission, allowing stolen plutonium to fall into the wrong hands. Now, he must partner with a hard-hitting CIA agent (Henry Cavill) in a race against time to stop a nuclear threat.

name: Khaleja
description: The story revolves around a remote village in Andhra Pradesh plagued by a strange disease killing a lot of people. The soothsayer of the village predicts that God would come to their village for rescue. Meanwhile, Raju (Mahesh Babu) a cab driver in Hyderabad goes to Rajasthan to handover an insurance cheque to a man's family who dies in his car. In a strange situation,

name: Dehati Ladke - Season 2
description: Rajat's tumultuous journey of love, friendship, and self-discovery unfolds as he navigates the aftermath of a painful breakup with Prerna. Distraught, he vents his emotions by inscribing derogatory remarks about her on currency notes, inadvertently triggering a campus-wide scandal.

name: Jab Tak Hai Jaan
description: Samar (Shah Rukh Khan) meets Meera (Katrina Kaif) in London & they fall in love. Samar however meets with a serious accident & Meera vows to God to leave Samar, if He allowed him to live. Samar angered with God, becomes a bomb disposal chief in the Indian Army. Here he meets Akira (Anushka Sharma). Is Akira able to unravel the mysteries, does Samar win the battle, or does God surrender to his love?

name: Vivah
description: Pooja, an orphan, is to wed Prem, the son of a wealthy family. With the wedding day approaching, both families start their respective preparations, not knowing that fate has other plans in store.

name: SPREAD a.k.a. TOYBOY
description: A sex comedy centered on a serial womanizer and his jilted lover. In Los Angeles, Nikki is homeless, car-less and closing in on 30, but he's good-looking, moving from one wealthy woman of 35 or 40 to another, a kept boy-toy. His newest gig is Samantha, an attorney. Then Nikki meets Heather, a waitress. Is the player being played, or might this be love? What will Nikki discover?

name: Jumanji: The Next Level
description: In Jumanji:The Next Level, the gang is back (Dwayne Johnson, Jack Black, Kevin Hart and Karen Gillan) but the game has changed.

name: Welcome
description: Two dons want their sister to get married. They find a suitable match, but the groom's uncle wants him to get married to a girl from a decent family. The only way they can get married is, if both the dons give up their life of crime.

name: A Nice Girl Like You
description: After being accused of being too inhibited by her ex-boyfriend, a violinist creates a rather wild to-do list that sends her on a whirlwind journey of self-discovery.

name: The Mummy
description: Nick and Corporal Chris stumble upon the tomb of Princess Ahmanet during an air strike.

name: Wrong Turn : The Foundation
description: Friends lost during hiking the Appalachian Trail are confronted by 'The Foundation', a community of cultists who have lived in the mountains for hundreds of years. The cultists attack them in a terrifying game of hide and seek and twists and turns

name: Tatsama Tadbhava
description: A seasoned police inspector delves into a perplexing missing person's investigation that reveals a web of secrets, lies, and mystery.

name: BIHTER: A FORBIDDEN PASSION
description: Amazon Original movie from Turkey unlocks a new perspective on Halid Ziya Uşaklıgil’s novel, Aşk-ı Memnu (Forbidden Love). Explore the love by diving into the thoughts of the heroine. Bihter sees marrying rich but elderly Adnan an escape from societies labels. However Bihter is engulfed by desires for Behlül, a relative of Adnan. Bihter is the story of passion, infidelity, courage, and cowardice.

name: Month of Madhu
description: A 19 year, Indian origin girl, born in the US, visits Vizag to attend a cousin's wedding. In her search for freedom, she embarks on a 1 month journey with a 42 year carefree, directionless man who is on the verge of divorce with his wife Lekha. This beautiful tale of Madhumathi, Madhusudan Rao and Lekha talks of relationships, perceptions, freedom, love and life.

name: King Kong
description: A film producer sets out to capture a giant ape.

name: 12 Strong
description: The True Story of the Army's Special Forces "Green Berets", who within weeks responded to the 9-11 attack. Green Berets and AFSOC took over the country and allowed other Special Forces and the rest of the conventional military to begin the real war.

name: Guy Ritchie's The Covenant
description: Follows Sergeant John Kinley, who on his last tour of duty in Afghanistan is teamed with local interpreter Ahmed, who risks his own life to carry an injured John across miles of grueling terrain to safety.

name: Jurassic Park III (4K UHD)
description: Adventure runs wild when renowned paleontologist Dr. Alan Grant (Sam Neill) agrees to accompany a wealthy adventurer (William H. Macy) and his wife (Téa Leoni) on an aerial tour of Isla Sorna, InGen's former breeding ground for prehistoric creatures.

name: Vinaya Vidheya Rama
description: When the happiness of his family is held to ransom by a violent crime lord, Ram sets out on a quest to destroy his nemesis and his criminal empire.

name: Hera Pheri
description: Three unemployed men find the answer to all their money problems when they recieve a call from a kidnapper. However, things do not go as planned.

name: Aspirants - Season 2
description: Abhilash has assumed the position of District Magistrate in Rampur. The emergence of ideological disparities between Abhilash and ALC Sandeep Ohlan has resulted in escalating tensions between them.

name: Beautiful Disaster
description: Abby, a college freshman, is eager to focus on her studies and start a new social life. Her plans are quickly derailed when she meets Travis, a bad-boy brawler and campus charmer. While she tries to resist her attraction to him, Travis offers her a simple bet that makes them roommates for a month.

name: The Village - Season 1
description: In the desolate hinterlands of Tamil Nadu, a stranded urbanite enlists the help of three locals to find his missing family believed to have been abducted by nefarious beings of a cursed village. Meanwhile, a maniacal heir to a pharma empire sends a group of mercenaries to the same village to retrieve something long forgotten. Will they come out of this terror-stricken night alive?

name: Padmaavat
description: Set in 1303 AD medieval India, Padmaavat is the story of honor, valor and obsession. Queen Padmavati is known for her exceptional beauty along with a strong sense of justice and is the wife of Maharawal Ratan Singh and pride of the Kingdom of Chittor, a prosperous kingdom in the north west of India. The legend of her beauty reaches the reigning sultan of Hindustan – Allaudin Khilji.

name: Pranaam
description: Ajay, an honest and hardworking college-goer dreams of fulfilling his father's long-held ambition of becoming an IAS officer and toils hard to achieve it. But an encounter with a local goon Gyanu Singh forces him to turn to the path of crime and become a gangster.

name: Fukrey 3
description: In the third installment, the Fukras plan to take over Delhi, and run for city elections. However, they have no money and so they take on an international job to make a quick buck, which changes their lives forever. In the first two films, we saw them using dreams, then premonitions to make money but now they’ve been gifted with a new & unique talent which is going to make them millionaires.

name: Kalank
description: Set in 1945, in Pre-Independent India, ‘Kalank’ is the story of a vivid and ethereal world, lost when the fire of Partition engulfs the city and the country. It’s the story of the shades of Reds in their lives as they yearn for hues of love while Husnabad gets soaked in the reds of violence and revenge.

name: Vishal in Laatti Charge
description: A police constable, who gets trapped in a building with his 10-year-old kid, and how they escape from the building surrounded by a group of the enemy.

name: Hereditary
description: After the death of her mentally ill mother, a woman and her family uncover their evil lineage.

name: Munna Bhai M.B.B.S.
description: Munna Bhai M.B.B.S. Is A National Award Winning Bollywood Comedy Hindi Movie, Directed By Rajkumar Hirani, Starring Sanjay Dutt And Arshad Warsi In The Lead Roles. The Film Won 18 Awards. Munna Is A Goon Who Sets Out To Fulfill His Father's Dream Of Becoming A Doctor. With Help From His Sidekick Circuit, He Enrolls Himself In Medical College And Drives Dr Asthana Up The Wall.

name: JHIMMA
description: 7 women from different age groups and different socio-cultural backgrounds come together on a vacation with a tour company to ENGLAND. During the course of this trip these women unfold their journey. This trip turns into an opportunity to mend fences, heal wounds, fall in love with themselves, combat their worst fears and celebrate life.

name: X
description: In 1979, a group of young filmmakers set out to make an adult film in rural Texas, but when their reclusive, elderly hosts catch them in the act, the cast find themselves fighting for their lives.

name: Spider-Man: Far From Home
description: Following the events of Avengers: Endgame, Spider-Man must step up to take on new threats in a world that has changed forever.

name: Fukrey
description: The story revolves around four suboptimal individuals who are struggling to cope up with studies and their personal desires to make it big. Their hunger for success leads them to indulge in unacceptable situations and are soon forced to face mind-twisting and complicated obstacles which make their troubled life even harder. Will they overcome these situations and see the light?

name: Mardaani 2
description: A 21-year old boy named Sunny (Vishal Jethwa), comes to the city on a murder contract. But he also has a penchant for sexually assaulting and murdering young girls. When he locks horns with Shivani Shivaji Roy (Rani Mukerji), the newly appointed Chief of the city police, a thrilling cat and mouse hunt begins. Will Shivani manage to nab Sunny, or does she end up being one of his many victims?

name: Dear Sathya (Hindi)
description: Dear Sathya is a Hindi dubbed version of a Kannada revenge action thriller. Food delivery boy Sathya is in love with Anjali, a restaurant employee who is also an aspiring air hostess. But then a tragedy occurs for the couple and Sathya is arrested as a suspect in the case. Can Sathya find out the truth and bring justice to Anjali?

name: Any How Mitti Pao
description: Any How Mitti Pao,' is a comedy story that explores the power of friendship, about the bond between two friends, Harry and Jeeta. they have been performing in the theatre group, However, the group is in trouble and faces financial difficulties. they approach a rich man.Unfortunately, he rejects the proposal and mocks their talent. Both Friends to swindle the wealthy with their creativity their art

name: Spider-Man: Into the Spider-Verse
description: “Spider-Man: Into the Spider-Verse” introduces Brooklyn teen Miles Morales, and the limitless possibilities of the Spider-Verse, where more than one can wear the mask.

name: Sapta Sagaradaache Ello - Side A
description: In the heart of 'Sapta Sagaradaache Ello’ (Somewhere Beyond the Seven Seas), lies an ardent love story between Manu & Priya. Their journey, set against the backdrop of a city's shadows, delves into the depths of their emotions. In a world where promises hold weight and fate’s grasp is firm, how far will Manu go to fulfil his promise? What becomes of love when destiny triggers an unexpected turn?

name: Kandahar
description: A CIA Black Ops agent and his Afghan interpreter must evade deadly forces as they escape Iran after a whistleblower reveals the agent destroyed a nuclear facility.

name: Majili
description: Poorna (Naga Chaitanya) is a youth from Vizag who falls in love with Anju (Divyansha Kaushik), a rich naval officer's daughter. As time passes by, Poorna's local politics create a rift in their love story & they break apart. Moving ahead, Poorna marries Shravani (Samantha) but does not forget his love for Anu. Will the problems between the couple get resolved? How does the change happen?

name: Changure Bangaruraja
description: Follows Mangaratnam, Tatarao, and Gateelu. They changed the life of Veerabobbili, a dog. Things go smoothly for them until they become suspects in a murder.

name: Theeppori Benny
description: Theeppori Benny is a family comedy entertainer set on political satire about the conflicts between Vattakkuttayil Chettayi, a selfless communist and his son, Vattakkuttayil Benny, who loathes politics and politicians. The story takes a turn when Benny accidentally steps into politics. How both their political views changes when the father-son due grow closer is the rest of the story.

name: Godzilla vs. Kong
description: Godzilla and Kong clash in a battle for the ages. As Monarch embarks on a mission into uncharted terrain, a human conspiracy threatens to wipe the creatures from the face of the earth.

name: Kabhi Khushi Kabhie Gham
description: Yashvardhan Raichand is a snobbish man, he breaks ties with his elder son Rahul, for marrying a girl with lower social status. When his younger son Rohan returns home, he is upset to know that his brother no longer lives with them. Rohan decides to reunite his family and goes to London and finds Rahul. But, the question is will he be successful in convincing his egoistic father for a reunion?

name: ROOM 203
description: Many residents of ROOM 203 have disappeared since the murder suicide of a married couple exactly fifty years ago. Lifelong friends Kim and Izzy and roommates are terrified by the vengeful spirits dwelling in their apartment. To save Izzy's life, Kim may need to sacrifice her own. Based on the Internationally Bestselling novel by Kamon Nanami.

name: MAD
description: Maddy(Madhav Chilukuri) is a playboy by nature. On the other hand, Madhuri(Spandana) is a girl who believes in true love. What happens when people with such different ideologies get married. What problems do they face?

name: The Expendables 4
description: A new generation of stars join the world's top action stars for an adrenaline-fueled adventure. Armed with every weapon they can get their hands on and the skills to use them, The Expendables are the world's last line of defense and the team that gets called when all other options are off the table. But new team members with new styles and tactics are going to give "new blood" a whole new meaning.

name: Dada (Hindi)
description: Manikandan and Sindhu, college lovers, face an unexpected pregnancy. Amidst Manikandan's drinking problem, their relationship crumbles. But Manikandan's life changes forever when Sindhu vanishes after giving birth, leaving the baby behind.

name: Rakshak India's Braves
description: Inspired by true events, "Rakshak - India's Braves" is the story of Triveni Singh, an Indian Army Lieutenant who is devoted to his family, but his passion to save people around him from threats is far more noble and greater. What starts off as a threat of a militant attack soon turns into something far threatening.

name: Guthlee Ladoo
description: Guthlee, son of a poor sweeper, has a dream - to go to school. But the obstacle is his caste. A headmaster is sympathetic to him but powerless against caste discrimination. When they develop an unspoken bond, Guthlee's dream sees hope.

name: Jurassic World: Fallen Kingdom
description: Owen and Claire return to the ruins of the Jurassic World theme park to rescue the remaining dinosaurs from a looming volcanic extinction.

name: Paramporul
description: A struggling youngster (Amithash) crosses paths with an eccentric police officer (R. Sarathkumar) during a theft , after which they get sucked into the dangerous world of Idol Smuggling. A game of cat and mouse ensues in the backdrop of a bigger danger.

name: Vodka Diaries
description: A series of mysterious murders suddenly takes place in a single night in Manali. ACP Ashwini Dixit starts investigation in order to solve the same sensing that it might be connected to the night club named Vodka Diaries.

name: Dhoom:2
description: Dhoom:2 reinvents the action comedy genre and propels it into the 21st century. Ali (Uday Chopra) is now ACP Jai Dixit’s (Abhishek Bachchan) right-hand man. Enter Mr.A (Hrithik Roshan), a high tech international thief whose next target is Mumbai. Once in Mumbai, Mr.A finds his match in Sunehri (Aishwarya Rai), a clever thief. She makes him an offer he finds hard to refuse. And so the game begins.

name: Fall
description: For best friends Becky and Hunter, life is all about conquering fears and pushing limits. However, after they climb 2,000 feet to the top of a remote, abandoned radio tower, they find themselves stranded with no way down. Now, their expert climbing skills are put to the ultimate test as they desperately fight to survive the elements, a lack of supplies, and vertigo-inducing heights.

name: Dear Comrade
description: Dear Comrade is an intense love story between Bobby (Vijay Deverakonda), a student union leader and Lily (Rashmika Mandanna) a state-level cricketer. Bobby has anger management issues, which he needs to overcome and fight for his love.

name: Baanadariyalli
description: Bound only by their love for Leela, two strangers find themselves in the beautiful wilderness of Kenya traversing new landscapes, fighting danger and eachother. This is not a Love Story, this is a Story about Love.

name: Zakir Khan: Kaksha Gyarvi
description: Zakir Khan is back, and this time he takes you down the memory lane by reminiscing about school, friends and everything that era signified for Zakir. Right from survival to bullying he shares every hysterical and amusing story from his book of memories.

name: About My Father
description: Encouraged by his fiancee, a man and his father spend the weekend with her wealthy and exceedingly eccentric family. The gathering soon develops into a culture clash, allowing father and son to discover the true meaning of family.

name: Boyz 4
description: Dhungya and Dhairya top the junior college exam, but Kabir drops out of the college, and continues his higher education abroad. He breaks off their friendship and challenges his old friends to visit him in London to settle the score. Dhungya and Dhairya get their chance to do exactly that, as part of the foreign cultural exchange program.

name: The Lair
description: Shot down over one of the most dangerous rebel strongholds in Afghanistan, a Royal Air Force pilot discovers an abandoned Soviet Research Facility concealed in the remote hills. She finds refuge in an underground bunker where deadly man-made biological weapons - half human, half alien and hungry for human flesh are awakened as she watches the creatures rip apart the men pursuing her.

name: Bharat Ane Nenu
description: Bharath (Mahesh Babu) who comes down to attend the sudden demise of his father who was the Chief Minister of Andhra Pradesh is forced to become the CM himself. He is not happy with the way government is functioning in the state and wants to bring in monumental changes in it’s operations. The number of people opposing him only grows day by day forcing him to take a few strong decisions.

name: Captain Prabhakaran
description: Prabhakaran, an Indian Forest Service (IFS) officer, is sent to Sathyamangalam to nab the notorious smuggler, Veerabhadran. He was not only going to nab him, but also avenge the death of his friend.

name: One Day: Justice Delivered
description: After Judge Tyagi retires, certain people go missing mysteriously. Things get complicated when crime branch officer Rathi investigates the cases and makes shocking revelations.

name: Phir Hera Pheri
description: Baburao, Raju, and Shyam are living happily after having risen from rags to riches. Still, money brings the joy of riches and with it the greed to make more money. And so, with a don as an unknowing investor, Raju initiates a new game.

name: Smugglers
description: 1970s, at Guncheon, there were Haenyeos, including two best friends. They always collected seafood under water for living. But, as few factories started to be built near the beach, Haenyeos started to have trouble with what they were doing for living. Without any choice, the ship crews decided to join smuggling business in water to seek a way for their lives.

name: Mission: Impossible - Dead Reckoning Part One - Extended Preview
description: Check out the thrilling extended preview of Mission: Impossible – Dead Reckoning Part One starring Tom Cruise

name: Zanjeer
description: ACP Vijay Khanna is transferred to Mumbai where he will have to deal with the oil mafia led by Rudra Pratap Teja.

name: Harkara
description: A frustrated postman decides to fool innocent villagers in a ploy to get himself transferred. As he walks uphill to deliver his last letter, a wayfarer narrates to him the story of a Harkara, that instills guilt.

name: The Wandering Earth II
description: Humans built huge engines on the surface of the earth to find a new home. But the road to the universe is perilous. In order to save earth, young people once again have to step forward to start a race against time for life and death.

name: Dabangg 3
description: Dabangg 3 is a high-voltage tongue-in-cheek story of a famous cop, Chulbul Pandey, an Uttar Pradesh cop who calls himself Robin Hood Pandey. Things take an unexpected turn when his past comes to haunt him as the face of the main antagonist of the film, Balli. Circumstances force Chulbul to take up the righteous path to protect his loved ones and family and do what is right in the eyes of the law.

name: Thalaivaa (Hindi)
description: Vishwa is a dancer in Sydney and runs a small business. He is unaware that his father is a gangster in Mumbai. When Vishwa visits India to seek his blessings for marriage, his life turns upside down.

name: The Ghazi Attack (Hindi)
description: Inspired by true events, The Ghazi Attack is India's first underwater war film. The story revolves around the events that unfolded right before the Indo-Pakistan war of 1971, when the Pakistani Submarine Ghazi (Asia's most powerful fast-attack submarine at the time) attempted to destroy the Indian aircraft carrier Vikrant.

name: How to Train Your Dragon 2
description: This thrilling second chapter of the How to Train Your Dragon trilogy returns to the fantastical world of Hiccup and Toothless as they unite to save the future of men and dragons!

name: Shot Boot Three
description: A new pet friend "MAX" enters the lives of four kids bringing great joy. When Max is not to be found one day, the kids embark on a journey to find him, encountering experiences on the way that shape their understanding of life and their personalities.

name: Jailer
description: Tiger Muthuvel Pandian, a retired jailer, is now a family man who leads an ordinary life. Trouble knocks on his door when his son, a diligent cop, investigates an idol smuggling mafia. And forces Muthuvel Pandian to step back into the dark world of his past.

name: A Death in the Gunj
description: Set in 1979, A Death in the Gunj is a coming of age story, about a shy student Shutu who uses a family trip to escape from his failed semester. Shutus' quiet unraveling is overlooked by his family until the holiday ends with an implosion.

name: The Vow
description: Against all odds, a young man must win back his wife's love after she loses her memory in a car accident.

name: Chakravyuham: The Trap
description: Siri, a business partner and a housewife, was found with her throat slit. Ajay, the investigation officer tries to solve the case. Can he figure out who killed her and why?

name: Love and Life
description: A heartbroken recent widow, a marriage in trouble, and an uncertain romance... These three women, friends from way back when, may seem to live perfect lives in a perfect world but recently they have all struggled to remember love and to keep love alive. They learn, that when everything else fails, as long as you have your friends you have hope.

name: Ponmagal Vandhal
description: Ponmagal Vandhal is a murder mystery courtroom drama set in Ooty, in 2020. Venba (Jyotika), a determined lawyer, reopens the case of a serial killer Jothi after 15 Years. This is Venba’s journey against child abuse and her quest for justice.

name: HACK Crimes Online - Season 1
description: The season initially focuses on Shakti's induction in the cybercrime unit alongside Jigar and Girish, and how they transform into an indomitable force solving extreme cybercrime cases under the tutelage of ACP Ashutosh.

name: Rocky Aur Rani Kii Prem Kahaani
description: A rollercoaster journey taking you through an epic love story in a new-age era, topped with hearty laughs and posing questions about love, family and the meaning of breaking away from generations of family traditions in the name of love.

name: RAAGHU
description: A medicine delivery executive working at night shift loots the houses he delivers. An unexpected incident forces him to accomplish a few crooked deals overnight failing to which his life may go upside down

name: Bedurulanka 2012
description: Bhushanam (Ajay Ghosh) and his gang try to take advantage of the people who are worried about the possible apocalypse on December 21, 2012. But Shiva (Kartikeya), belonging to the village, tries to upset the apple cart. Shiva takes the help of his friends and ladylove Chitra (Neha Sshetty) for the same. How Shiva exposes the true colors of Bhushanam and his gang forms the crux of the story.

name: Ponniyin Selvan Part 2 (Hindi)
description: 968 AD. The Pandyan assassins gather once again to destroy the Chola dynasty. Now the mighty Chola princes must fight the Pandyas, the Rashtrakutas and other Chola enemies who have joined forces. Also, at play are the rumours of Ponniyin Selvan’s death at sea, the powerful Pazhuvettarayar’s betrayal, and the tragic destiny of Aditha Karikalan, whose heart was long lost to the vengeful Nandini.

name: The Silence of the Lambs
description: Based on the novel by Thomas Harris.

name: Masti Express
description: Masti Express Is A Hindi Comedy Movie, Directed By Vikram Pradhan, Starring Rajpal Yadav And Johnny Lever In The Lead Roles. An Auto Rickshaw Driver, Raju, Wants His Son To Have The Best Education. He Seizes The Opportunity To Win A Large Sum Of Money In A Racing Contest.

name: Sleeping with Other People
description: Jake (Jason Sudeikis) and Lainey (Alison Brie) impulsively lose their virginity to each other in college.  When their paths cross twelve years later in New York City, they realize they both have become serial cheaters.  Bonding over their chronic commitment issues, they form a platonic friendship to support each other in their quests for healthy romantic relationships.

name: Chinese Zodiac
description: A man searches the world for a set of mystic artifacts. The twelve bronze heads of the animals from the Chinese zodiac.

name: The Batman
description: A killer targets Gotham's elite sending Batman on an investigation. As evidence mounts, he must forge new relationships, unmask the culprit, and bring justice to corruption.

name: Bambai Meri Jaan - Season 1
description: Bambai Meri Jaan chronicles the life of gangster Dara Kadri through the eyes of his father, an ex-cop, Ismail Kadri. In this season, we see how Dara puts everything on the line, including his family. He goes on to become a cold-blooded, fearless gangster who uses his business acumen to fight not only the police and his rivals but also his own demons along the way.

name: TERRITORY
description: In rural Vidarbha, a Tiger reserve, Local forest officer, Jiddewar, is investigating the case of a missing Tiger Jai from the reserve. Forest Officer suspects the case of poaching tigers is the act of an insider, a local group of people. But DYSP is sure it's the migrants but when they peel each layer of this multifaceted case, the truth that comes to light is uglier than their imagination.

name: Before the Rains ( In Hindi )
description: It's a melodrama about adultery between a British man and an Indian maid, set against the backdrop of British India in 1937.   T.K. works for a British employer and feels futile to support the freedom movement. As time passes, he realizes the need for independence and has to rethink about his decision.

name: Smile
description: After witnessing a bizarre, traumatic incident involving a patient, Dr. Rose Cotter (Sosie Bacon) starts experiencing frightening occurrences that she can't explain. As an overwhelming terror begins taking over her life, Rose must confront her troubling past in order to survive and escape her horrifying new reality.

name: Khamoshi
description: Khamoshi Is A Hindi Horror Thriller Movie, Directed By Chakri Toleti, Starring Tamannaah, Prabhu Deva And Bhumika Chawla In The Lead Roles. A Young Woman, Who Lives Alone And Has A Speech And Hearing Disability, Attempts To Save Herself When A Killer Appears At Her Doorstep. This Movie Based On Hush By Mike Flanagan.

name: My Client's Wife
description: Manas Verma, a lawyer, is defending Raghuram Singh who is accused of assaulting his wife. However, Raghuram claims that he is being framed. Verma then decides to get to the bottom of his client's case and uncover a shocking truth.

name: Savyasachi
description: A bus carrying 21 passengers meets an accident and the protagonist survives in the accident. His left hand is controlled by his twin brother, who was absorbed due to Vanishing Twin Syndrome. His family is attacked and his beloved niece is kidnapped. His twin brother becomes his strength and finally they come out of this situation.

name: Casino Royale
description: Based on Ian Fleming's first 007 novel, James Bond must thwart a dangerous Russian spy who is funding global terrorists from winning a baccarat game worth millions. The 21st film in the most successful film series in cinematic history.

name: Mission: Impossible - Rogue Nation
description: With his organization shut down, agent Ethan Hunt and his team race against time to stop a dangerous network of rogue operatives turned traitors. To defeat them, he must join forces with an elusive agent as he faces his most impossible mission yet.

name: Zakir Khan: Haq Se Single
description: In Haq Se Single, Zakir's narrative takes you through his own journey of becoming the ultimate #SakhtLaunda. The guy who's survived rejection, love, heart breaks and adulthood - who's single and proud of it!

name: JugJugg Jeeyo
description: “JugJugg Jeeyo” is a story set in Patiala that’s about love, laughter, colour and drama. After a lifelong friendship and a 5 year marriage, Kuku and Naina need to tell their family that they want a divorce. However, Kuku’s parents, Bheem and Geeta have other plans set in store for them; all this amidst his sister’s wedding. It’s about family, values, unresolved yearnings and unexpected reunions.

name: Aspirants - Season 1
description: It is the story of the journey of three UPSC Aspirants and their friendship against all odds.

name: To Catch a Killer
description: Baltimore. New Year's Eve. A talented but troubled police officer (Shailene Woodley) is recruited by the FBI's chief investigator (Ben Mendelsohn) to help profile and track down a disturbed individual terrorizing the city.

name: Flames - Season 1
description: A teenage romance that aims straight from the heart. This is the story of a young romance unfolding as a chemical reaction.

name: Skyfall
description: James Bond's loyalty to M is tested when her past comes back to haunt her. When MI6 comes under attack, 007 must track down and destroy the threat, no matter how personal the cost.

name: Jurassic World
description: The park is open.

name: Spectre
description: A cryptic message from James Bond's past sends him on a trail to uncover the existence of a sinister organisation named SPECTRE. With a new threat dawning, Bond learns the terrible truth about the author of all his pain in his most recent missions.

name: Jurassic Attack aka Rise of the Dinosaurs
description: A group of soldiers attempting to rescue a hostage from a terrorist crash land into unfamiliar jungles which are inhabited by a group of long hidden dinosaurs. Now they must find a way out of this isolated valley before becoming prey for prehistoric predators.

name: Jalebi - The Taste of Everlasting Love
description: Jalebi is the story of a one-book wonder Aisha Pradhan, who boards an overnight train journey from Mumbai to Delhi. As luck might have it, she gets stuck in the compartment with her former lover and his current wife. This is the story of how she battles all those unanswered questions from her strenuous past with Dev, the love of her life.

name: Sila Nodigalil
description: When a married cosmetic surgeon Raj Varadhan's girlfriend Maya Pillai accidentally dies of an overdose, his life takes him on an unexpected ride. Will he be able to hide his secrets from his wife Medha Varadhan?

name: Gen V - Season 1
description: From the world of The Boys comes Gen V, a thrilling new series set at America’s only college for superheroes. These gifted students put their moral boundaries to the test, competing for the university’s top ranking, and a chance to join The Seven, Vought International’s elite superhero team. When the school’s dark secrets come to light, they must decide what kind of heroes they want to become.

name: No Strings Attached
description: A hilarious story about Emma and Adam who set up a seemingly perfect arrangement with each other based soley on sex and having only one cardinal rule: No Strings Attached.

name: John Wick: Chapter 4
description: John Wick (Keanu Reeves) uncovers a path to defeating The High Table. But before he can earn his freedom, Wick must face off against a new enemy with powerful alliances across the globe and forces that turn old friends into foes.

name: Baa Baaa Black Sheep
description: Baa Baaa Black Sheep Is A Bollywood Action Crime Hindi Romantic Movie, Directed By Vishwas Paandya, Starring Anupam Kher, Manish Paul, Annu Kapoor, Manjari Phadnis And Kay Kay Menon In The Lead Roles. Baba's 25th Birthday Shocks Him As He Comes To Know That He Has To Take Over His 12 Generations Old Family Business Of Assassination. He Falls In Love With Angelina, Who Has Secrets Of Her Own.

name: The Late Bloomer
description: The story of an adult male who, after the successful removal of a benign tumor resting against his pituitary gland, experiences all the changes and effects of puberty over a three-week period.

name: Eternal Sunshine of the Spotless Mind
description: A doctors invention allows a couple to erase the memories of their previous relationship.

name: Penguins of Madagascar
description: Plucky paramilitary penguins have exciting adventures.

name: Kanjoos Majnu Kharchili Laila  (Hindi)
description: A misery young man who falls in love with a middle-class girl who wishes to enjoy all the finer things in life and has big dreams of a high-flying and jet-setting lifestyle.

name: Ravanasura (Hindi)
description: When ACP is assigned to investigate a spate of grizzly murders, he suspects goofy junior criminal lawyer may have a dark side.

name: Yaadhum Oore Yaavarum Kelir
description: A refugee struggles hard to find an identity for himself in order to accomplish his dreams.

name: Valerian and the City of a Thousand Planets
description: A dark force threatens Alpha, a vast metropolis and home to species from a thousand planets. Special operatives Valerian and Laureline must race to identify the marauding menace and safeguard not just Alpha, but the future of the universe.

name: Subhedar
description: We all revere Tanaji Malusare for the enormous courage he displayed during the battle of Sinhagad, and his ultimate sacrifice for the great cause of Swarajya. However, this grand battle was only a small part of the achievements of Subhedar Tanaji Malusare, a commander in the service of the great king Shivaji. This is his story.

name: Sherlock: Series 1
description: Sherlock Holmes and Doctor Watson's adventures arrive in 21st Century London.

name: How To Be Single
description: Dakota Johnson and Rebel Wilson headline a stellar cast in this comedy about a group of unmarried New Yorkers learning the "right way" to be single.

name: Top Gun
description: Cocky fighter pilot Maverick (Tom Cruise) refuses to conform to the collaborative environment at the elite Naval Fighter Weapons School. Maverick’s talent is undeniable, but the consequences of being a renegade could cost him his career.

name: The Hunger Games
description: First installment in the epic “Hunger Games” series. Teenage Katniss Everdeen voluntarily replaces her sister in a brutal and deathly competition.

name: Gandhigiri
description: An NRI Rai Saheb (Om Puri) strongly believes in the principles of Mahatma Gandhi. After returning to India, he comes across four troubled people who've made wrong choices in life. The movie captures his efforts to reform them by following Gandhiji's example.

name: Ninja: Shadow of a Tear
description: Martial artist Casey Bowman decides to settle down with his pregnant wife, Namiko. However, he soon sets out on a bloody quest for vengeance after she is killed by a group of muggers.

name: The Secret Life of Pets
description: A terrier and his canine pal encounter a rebellious bunny and his gang of abandoned pets.

name: Dil To Pagal Hai
description: DIL TO PAGAL HAI is the story of Rahul (Shahrukh Khan), who does not believe in love. It is the story of Pooja (Madhuri Dixit), who believes that there is someone who is made for her & she is destined to meet that person. It is the story of Nisha (Karisma Kapoor) who believes that love is friendship & one day her dream will come true. It makes us believe that - someone somewhere is made for us.

name: Shaolin Soccer
description: Un joven seguidor de Shaolin se reúne con sus hermanos desanimados para formar un equipo de fútbol usando sus habilidades en artes marciales a su favor. Para ello también reclutará a una mujer con extraordinarias habilidades de kung fu.

name: Ghajini
description: Ghajini Is An Award Winning Bollywood Action Thriller Hindi Movie, Directed By A. R. Murugadoss, Starring Aamir Khan, Asin Thottumkal, Jiah Khan And Pradeep Rawat In The Lead Roles. A Tycoon, Suffering From Acute Short-term Memory Loss, Cannot Remember Anything Beyond Fifteen Minutes. With A Bunch Of Polaroids And Tattoos On His Body, He Sets Out To Find His Lover's Killer.

name: Hunterrr
description: An ordinary guy with a questionable reputation is obsessed with sex and chases girls until he falls in love and decides to settle down. But will the girl of his dreams reciprocate his feelings? What will happen when his past comes knocking on his door?

name: Student of the Year 2
description: Rohan (Tiger Shroff) is a student, athlete from a mediocre Pishorilal Chamandas College. He dreams of becoming the Student of the Year one day. His life takes a turn, when he gets accepted to St. Teresa College, encounters his rival Manav & has the beautiful Shreya and Mia who begin to fall for him. Their life gets tangled through competition, failure, manipulation and heartbreaks.

name: Arrival
description: Linguistics professor Louise Banks leads an elite team of investigators when gigantic spaceships touch down in 12 locations around the world. Banks and her crew must race against time to find a way to communicate with the extraterrestrial visitors. Hoping to unravel the mystery, she takes a chance that could threaten her life and quite possibly all of mankind.

name: Young Sheldon - Season 5
description: [NEW EPISODES WEEKLY] For young Sheldon Cooper, it isn't easy growing up in East Texas. Being a once-in-a-generation mind capable of advanced mathematics and science isn't always helpful in a land where church and football are king. And while the vulnerable, gifted and somewhat naïve Sheldon deals with the world, his very normal family must find a way to deal with him

name: Adrishyam
description: A drama-thriller film. Concurrent misfortunes of a murder, a kidnapping, and an accident induce unrelated teams to investigate with contradictory leads. The climax unravels the truth behind these incidents. The anticipated suspense keeps the viewer at the edge during the entire process of the investigation

name: अंदाज अपना अपना
description: अमर और प्रेम दिन में सपने देखने वाले लोगों में से हैं, जिनका एक समान इरादा अमीर लड़कियों से शादी करके अमीर बनने का है। वे काफी उथल-पुथल के बीच अरबपतियों की बेटी का हाथ पाने की कोशिश करते हैं। आखिरकार, प्यार के लिए कोशिश करने वाले ये दोनों ही कामचोर, अनजाने में अमीर लड़की को खतरनाक अपराधी से बचाने वाले रक्षक बन जाते हैं।

name: Mera Bhai - Season 1
description: This series shows the love-hate relationship of two brothers who happen to have, totally poles apart personalities. Bittu (Elder brother) is in his final year of college and is preparing for his job placement. Sittu (Younger brother) is in class 10th and is way too chill to be giving board exams the same year. This show captures the most relatable yet hilarious nuances of BHAI-BHAI relation.

name: Contract
description: Contract is a 2008 Bollywood spy film written and directed by Ram Gopal Varma. The film is setup in the backdrop of terrorism, and the infiltration by R.A.W. and Intelligence Bureau. Starring Adhvik Mahajan, Upendra Limaye, Prasad Purandare, and Zakir Hussain in pivotal roles

name: Los Farad - Season 1
description: The day Oskar, a typical local boy, crosses paths with the mysterious and wealthy Farad family, his life changes forever. Oskar enters a winner-take-all game, the world of international arms trafficking. In Marbella where the Farads live, luxury, adrenaline and intense emotions await him... But also a backside of violence and cynicism that tests his will.

name: Special Agent
description: Special Agent is a 2020 Blockbuster South Korean Action movie that is based on Won-cheol of the National Intelligence Service of the Republic of Korea and is offered a mission. Eliminating VIPs who participated in the operation to develop weapons of mass destruction in North Korea. He is forced to accept the mission while thinking of her daughter who is in danger.

name: A (Ad infinitum)
description: It is a quest of a mysterious person for his past, which sets him off an increasingly convoluted quest that spans decades involving science, crime, and a political movement, facing a violent opposition from an equally obsessed medical pioneer, giving an edge of the seat thriller experience with a Never Before Storyline on Indian Cinema.

name: Mister Pregnant
description: Mr. Pregnant is a unique story about a young couple in Hyderabad who are trying to conceive. They succeed but the husband gets pregnant. How did this happen? Can a man actually give birth? Will society accept it?

name: Amala
description: The journey of a brilliant police officer who is entrusted with the task of solving a series of murders happening in the city overnight. He sets out to find clues that would lead him to the killer.

name: Bait
description: A freak tsunami traps shoppers at a coastal Australian supermarket inside the building - along with 12-foot Great White Sharks.

name: The Dictator - Rated
description: The creators and star of Borat bring you the jaw-dropping comedy about what happens when the world’s worst dictator comes to America. Get ready to laugh ?til it hurts with this outrageous and shamefully funny comedy!

name: Good Luck to You, Leo Grande
description: Two-time Oscar winner Emma Thompson (Nancy) is looking for some adventure, and some sex. Good sex. And she has a plan: she hires a young sex worker named Leo Grande. After three long decades of unsatisfying marital relations with the same man, can Nancy take control of her sex life and receive the longed-for pleasure she deserves?

name: Vasantha Kokila (Telugu)
description: Rudhran, who works tirelessly for a successful career and money, embarks on a romantic journey to spend quality time with his girlfriend Nila. On the way, he stays at the Vasantha Mullai Motel. The events that unfold in a single night drive Rudhran insane and take him on a roller coaster ride.

name: Mission: Impossible
description: Ethan Hunt, a secret agent, is framed for the deaths of his espionage team and attempts to flee government assassins after him. He races against the clock in order to discover the truth.

name: Mission Start Ab - Season 1
description: Mission Start Ab, a competitive reality series, sees three top investors handpick ten extraordinary early-stage founders. Throughout the series, they'll face relentless challenges that will test their entrepreneurial mettle. The last-standing founders get the chance of a lifetime: a potential investment in their startups. It's the dream deal every founder craves, and it's all on the line.

name: My Man is Cupid
description: Star-crossed love story between a love fairy and a human girl. For humans and fairies aren’t meant to be, when he accidentally shoots himself and falls in love, their fate takes a wrong turn. The two reconnect after centuries of reincarnation. Where will this story lead?

name: 21 Jump Street
description: Young cops go under cover as high-school students.

name: Congrats My Ex!
description: Risa (Bella Ranee Campen) and her friends, wedding planners on the brink of bankruptcy, reluctantly accept organizing an Indian wedding. Fate intervenes when the groom-to-be, Arun (Mahir Pandhi) is her ex-partner. To complicate matters, she is forced to recruit her other ex, Tim (Bright Vachirawit Chivaaree), as the wedding photographer. As chaos is assured, will they be able to make it through?

name: Viswasam
description: A village ruffian, who settles disputes in his native, takes on a big shot when he tries to sort out the rough patch in his marriage after several years.

name: Gupt: The Hidden Truth
description: Gupt: The Hidden Truth Is A Bollywood Award Winning Hindi Action Movie, Directed By Rajiv Rai, Starring Bobby Deol, Manisha Koirala, Kajol, Om Puri, Raj Babbar And Kulbhushan Kharbanda In The Lead Roles. Sahil Is Arrested For Murdering His Stepfather, But He Is Determined To Prove His Innocence. He Escapes From Jail With Help From Sheetal, But Inspector Udham Singh Is Hot On His Trail.

name: Sardaar Ji 2 (Hindi)
description: Jaggi, a farmer, travels to Australia in order to save his village. Once there, he is chased by a few goons and ultimately kidnaps a girl from her own wedding.

name: Golmaal Fun Unlimited
