name: Transformers: The Last Knight
description: Our world's greatest hero becomes our fiercest enemy when Optimus Prime launches a mission to save Cybertron by destroying Earth. Now Bumblebee and Cade Yeager (Mark Wahlberg) must lead the Autobots in the ultimate battle to save mankind.

name: Jaws
description: Academy Award-winner Steven Spielberg directs one of the most influential and gripping adventures in film history about the hunt of a deadly great white shark.

name: Pyaar Toh Hona Hi Tha
description: Rahul leaves Sanjana for a woman he meets in India but Sanjana refuses to give up. She hires Shekhar to pretend to be her boyfriend but in the process falls in love with him.

name: Aruvi
description: A gentle girl born and brought up amidst the ever growing eco-social-consumeristic environment finds it difficult to fit in the society. She decides to take it hard on the people. What she does is the rest of the story.

name: Guest iin London
description: Aryan is in a live-in relationship with his partner Anaya in London. However, problems arise when Gangasharan and Guddi, their uncle and aunt from India, come to their house uninvited.

name: Runaway Train
description: Escaped cons (Jon Voight, Eric Roberts) and girl (Rebecca De Mornay) on wild diesel in Alaska.

name: Bodyguard
description: Bodyguard is a 2020 Blockbuster Korean Action movie about a man who lost his love and his desire to live and came across a woman who was being chased by an unidentified assailant. She is the only heir of the corporation. And she has been chased by someone who was trying to deprive the company

name: Khatta Meetha
description: A seemingly corrupt petty contractor faces challenges from the local municipality, his family, his employees, as well as a former girlfriend and her family.

name: Besharam
description: Babli is a street-smart car mechanic living in a Delhi orphanage. He steals cars to support his orphanage. He has no sense of right or wrong, till he unwittingly hurts the love of his life & is chased by cop couple Chulbul & Bulbul Chautala. Babli realizes that there is no right way of doing the wrong thing. Babli sets out to fix all the wrongs in his life and he continues to be shameless about it

name: Aatagallu
description: Siddharth is a top director accused of brutally murdering his wife Anjali. Veerendra is appointed as public prosecutor in the case. He has a track record of supporting the right guy. All evidence point at Siddharth as the killer. What happens when Veerendra is convinced that Siddharth is not a murderer? Veerendra finds that what appeared a simple case takes on a darker, more dangerous aspect.

name: Fan
description: FAN is the story of Gaurav (Shah Rukh Khan) a young man, 20 something, whose world revolves around the mega movie star Aryan Khanna (Shah Rukh Khan) or God as he refers to him. When things don't go according to plan, Gaurav’s love and passion for his God turns into a dangerous obsession that crosses the fine line.

name: The Great Indian Family
description: The film is set in the fictional town of Balrampur where Vedvyas Tripathi (Vicky Kaushal) better known as Bhajan Kumar lives with his family headed by his father Pandit Siyaram Tripathi (Kumud Mishra). Bhajan Kumar’s life with his family was going well till a question on his identity arises that throws the city in a flurry of rumour and apprehension. Will he survive or fall prey to this onslaught?

name: Thappad
description: Thappad is a story of Amrita whose seemingly perfect life is shattered when her husband slaps her once in a party. But is one slap enough to question what a relationship stands for?

name: Memory
description: Alex, an assassin-for-hire, finds that he's become a target after he refuses to complete a job for a dangerous criminal organization. With the crime syndicate and FBI in hot pursuit, Alex has the skills to stay ahead, except for one thing: he is struggling with severe memory loss, affecting his every move. Alex must question his every action and whom he can ultimately trust.

name: Pari
description: Pari is a supernatural horror film in which a man attempts to help a woman named Ruksana, an abuse victim, who he found chained up in a hut.

name: A Scandall
description: A film crew explore a man's strange life of paranormal hallucinations of his deceased daughter and complete metamorphosis. However, their investigation uncovers secrets of murder, sex and incest.

name: Monica
description: Monica Is A Bollywood Hindi Thriller Movie, Directed By Sushen Bhatnagar, Starring Divya Dutta, Ashutosh Rana And Rajit Kapur In The Lead Roles. An Ambitious Girl Monica, Comes To The City From A Small Town To Become An Investigative Journalist. Situations Change When A Politician Industrialist Is Accused Of Killing Her.

name: Sorry Bhaisaab
description: This short film is a quirky tale of a middle-class couple, Varun and Kamla, residing in a typical DDA flats colony, their desires and aspirations just like that of any common middle-class family, learning the hard way that everything that is free, comes at its own cost.

name: The Divergent Series: Insurgent
description: A young woman must confront her inner demons and continue her fight against a powerful alliance.

name: Pacific Rim Uprising
description: John Boyega (Star Wars series) leads the cast in this cinematic epic of monsters and mechs, inspiring a new generation to become the biggest heroes to ever walk the earth.

name: Skyscraper
description: A former FBI agent on assignment in China is framed for a fire in the world's tallest building.

name: The Past
description: Two sisters Simran and Alia go on a vacation to Lonavala, where they experience paranormal activity at the bungalow that they're put up in, as an evil spirit takes over the place.

name: The World Is Not Enough
description: Bond takes position as bodyguard of a British oil tycoon's daughter after a deadly mishap at MI6.

name: Follow Me
description: #Love #Hate #Friends #Enemies #Live #Death. The line between real life and social media is blurred. A social media influencer travels to Moscow with his friends to capture new content for his successful VLOG, enters a deadly-life game filled with mystery and danger. Pushing the limits with growing audience, the group must fight to escape, and survive with unexpected deadly consequences.

name: Aame
description: Aame is the story of Kamini (Amala Paul), a vivacious and career conscious young lady who works in a TV channel. One morning, she finds herself lying completely naked in a deserted structure following a late-night party. Stark naked and having no phone to communicate, how she battles to get back safely and unlocks the mystery behind what happened that night makes up the rest of the film.

name: Tamizh Padam 2
description: A stringent cop tries all the possible ways to nab a dreaded don who poses a big threat to the society.

name: White Snake
description: White Snake Is A Kids Award Winning Animated Action Fantasy Romantic Film, One Day A Young Woman Named Blanca Is Saved By Xuan, A Snake Catcher From A Nearby Village. As They Set Off An A Journey To Discover Her Real Identity, The Pair Develop Feelings For Each Other. They Uncover A Darker Plot Of Supernatural Forces Vying For Power, With The Fate Of The World Hanging In The Balance.

name: Goodachari
description: After being trained in an ultra competitive secret service program, Arjun, A young agent is framed for the murder of his bosses, suddenly turning him into India's most wanted criminal. Who framed him? And why? For someone who was taught that the 'mission' is everything, Arjun now realizes that now his mission is darker than expected.

name: King Richard
description: Based on a true story. Richard Williams, father of legendary tennis champions Venus and Serena Williams, shows family and perseverance can achieve the impossible and impact the world.

name: Kabhi Alvida Naa Kehna
description: The movie sheds light on two suffocating marriages which depart lives and drift them towards an extramarital affair outside to fill the gap. Starring Shahrukh Khan, Abhishek, Preity and Rani in a romantic drama depicting true lives bounded in a relationship which has released its warmth over a period. Will these four be able to find their way out of their marriages or will accept their fate?

name: Spirit Doll
description: After a renowned horror actress, Dara Lazuardi, encounters a haunted doll resembling her deceased daughter, she becomes convinced of its connection to her child's spirit, leading her into a spiral of madness as others try to intervene.

name: Soorarai Pottru (Tamil)
description: Inspired by the book ‘Simply Fly’, the film tells the story of Nedumaaran Rajangam known to friends as Maara, the son of a teacher, who sets out to make the common man fly and takes on the most capital intensive industry in the world with the help of his friends, family and sheer will power.

name: Black Site
description: A group of officers in top secret prison must fight for their lives against Hatchet, a brilliant and infamous high value detainee. When he escapes, his mysterious and deadly agenda has far-reaching and dire consequences.

name: FORTRESS 2: SNIPER'S EYE
description: Retired CIA agent Robert and his son Paul have committed themselves to rebuild their relationship after their epic last encounter spent protecting the Fortress. When Paul's wife is abducted, he and Robert embark on a deadly mission to save her before time runs out.

name: Bheemadevarapally Branchi
description: Jampanna receives fifteen lakh rupees in his bank account, and assumes that he received money in his 'Zero Account' as promised by a political leader. Soon the bank claims that the money got transferred mistakenly but his family spends the money. Will Jampanna and his family be able to pay the money back?

name: Kaddha Chitra
description: Celebrity novelist, Vijay, writes his comeback novel about an innocent girl who falls prey to the deadly crimes of three men but is accused of plagiarism for the second time. What will he do?

name: Don 2
description: Don 2 is a sequel to a 2006's Indian action thriller 'Don'. Living in Thailand for past five years and having conquered the Asian underworld, international gangster Don (Shah Rukh Khan) now has bigger plans. Don has never been known to take the easy way out, but when he surrenders voluntarily to the Interpol in Malaysia, eyebrows are raised.

name: Pallu Padama Paathuka
description: Five youngsters, who are on the verge of committing suicide, happen to encounter zombies in a forest. Will they manage to escape?

name: xXx: Return of Xander Cage
description: When a group of lethal mercenaries steal a hi-tech weapon that poses a global threat, the world needs superspy Xander Cage. Recruited back into action, Xander leads a team of death-defying adrenaline junkies on a mission to save the world.

name: Hate Story 4
description: The girl who will stop at nothing to become a star model in the most coveted advertising agency in London, Tasha is ambitious, beautiful and without a doubt voluptuous. Rajveer, the man known to stop at nothing to get the woman he wants spots her talent and pitches her to get the project. Aryan, on the other hand, the man who is smitten by Tasha at first sight, will go beyond bonds and boundaries.

name: Goldeneye
description: Pierce Brosnan makes his debut as Bond in a furious chase to recover a stolen stealth helicopter and a lethal space weapon known as GoldenEye.

name: Batla House
description: An action thriller based on the 2008 police encounter in Delhi's Batla House.

name: Ittu Si Baat
description: Bittu Shukla, a small-town simpleton and aspiring cricketer, harbours a massive crush since childhood on his school friend Sapna. When Bittu learns his true-love's desires, he goes to great lengths to make them come true. Witness a sweet small town love story loaded with teenage innocence and a satirical comedy on the new age desire.

name: Viruman
description: Viruman leaves his house realizing that his father Muniyandi is the reason for his mother's suicide. Hence, father and son are at odds over everything.

name: Modern Love Chennai - Season 1
description: Modern Love Chennai is an eclectic bouquet of love stories – funny, quirky, deep and puzzling. While the stories converse with your heart, you also catch a glimpse into the soul of Chennai with its unique terrains and diverse inhabitants. Modern Love Chennai is inspired by articles published in the New York Times and has been adapted for the Tamil landscape.

name: No Country for Old Men
description: Violence and mayhem ensue after a hunter stumbles upon some dead bodies, a stash of heroin and more than $2 million in cash near the Rio Grande.

name: Teen Adkun Sitaram
description: Pushkar and Ajinkya are sons of political rivals. They are best friends with each other and with Kautilya from a middle class background.when they plan a trip to London to meet Pushkar’s girlfriend Reva, they prefer to keep their families in the dark. However, the trip turns into a nightmare when they are arrested by the London police on a drug charge.

name: Iqbal
description: Iqbal Is An Award Winning Hindi Sports Movie, Directed By Nagesh Kukunoor And Produced By Subhash Ghai, Starring Naseeruddin Shah, Shreyas Talpade And Girish Karnad In The Lead Roles. Iqbal, A Boy Hard Of Hearing And Without Speech, Dreams Of Playing In The Indian Cricket Team. When His Condition Hinders His Selection, He Asks A Retired Coach To Train Him.

name: Requiem for a Dream
description: Four people struggle against increasingly insatiable drug addictions. Despite their best intentions the drugs win as their lives spiral out of control.

name: The Huntsman: Winter's War
description: A huntsman and a fellow warrior battle an ice queen and her evil, resurrected sister.

name: Prassthanam
description: The film revolves around a politician Baldev Pratap Singh (Sanjay Dutt) and his family. When it comes to choosing his heir, Baldev chooses his stepson because he's a thinking man, eventually angering his own son and in the process triggering violence.

name: Ji Wife Ji
description: This film revolves around unblessed, unhappy and helpless husbands who are overpowered by their wives.

name: The Town (2010)
description: A bank robber falls in love with a former robbery hostage and decides he wants out of the life. With the Feds closing in he must choose: betray his friends or lose the woman he loves.

name: Hum Tum
description: Karan (Saif Ali Khan) is a cartoonist. His characters Hum and Tum reflect the strange love-hate relationship between men and women. Rhea (Rani Mukerji) is a sensitive, self-confident girl. Initially, they have very little in common. As life would have it, their paths keep crossing and over the course of a decade, their relationship evolves, from hate to mutual respect, friendship and finally love.

name: Get Out
description: A young man uncovers a dark secret when he meets his girlfriend's parents for the first time.

name: Watchmen
description: The year is 1985 and super heroes have banded together to respond to the murder of one of their own. They soon uncover a sinister plot that puts all of humanity in grave danger. The super heroes fight to stop the impending doom, only to find themselves a target for annihilation. But if our super heroes are gone, who will save us?

name: Bumblebee
description: Bumblebee the Autobot finds refuge in a California junkyard.

name: The Grotto
description: A young man is the sole survivor following a serious incident in a sealed-off cave. At the scene, four bodies were found and forensic scientists claim that this same man has murdered his friends, his wife and their tour guide. In hospital, he denies being a murderer and refuses to cooperate with the police. Sure that his wife was possessed by evil forces, he asks a nun for help.

name: Neyyattinkara Gopante Aaraattu
description: Aaraattu is set in a fictional village called Muthalakotta. The rustic serenity of the place is rattled by the arrival of Neyyattinkara Gopan, who is a rare mix of bravado and comic extravagance. The very purpose of his coming to the village undermines what the people there stand for. But their resistance withers layer by layer as Gopan weaves his spell on them.

name: Dulhan Hum Le Jayenge
description: Sapna is raised by her three uncles, each one of them with a contrasting pursuit in life. She falls in love with Raja, who tries to impress each of her uncles in a different manner.

name: House Of Darkness
description: Justin Long and Kate Bosworth star in this seductive thriller from director Neil LaBute (The Wicker Man). Driving home to her secluded estate after meeting at a local bar, a player out to score thinks his beautiful, mysterious date will be another casual hook-up. While getting acquainted, their flirtation turns playful, sexy and sinister. Hoping to get lucky, his luck may have just run out.

name: Picture This
description: Nerdy Mandy Gilbert has been invited to the biggest party of the year by the most popular boy at school. Just one problem...she’s grounded. No worries, though – Mandy and her pals have a plan. But will it work? Or will she end up grounded for life?

name: Howl
description: When passengers on a train are attacked by a creature, they must band together in order to survive until morning.

name: Bhouri
description: A 23-year-old girl who's married to a man more than twice her age is forced to contend with the predatory nature of a male-dominated society.

name: Suits
description: The third season premieres with a shift in the dynamics at the firm. After merging with a top British firm, Harvey is at odds with his boss and mentor, Jessica Pearson (Gina Torres), who forces Mike to do something he never thought possible - betray Harvey.

name: Kanjoos Family
description: Amit is a man with a plan; a plan to use his family money to start a business. But his family would rather let the money rot than to actually spend it. Calling them thrifty would be an understatement as they try to save every paisa. And this has made Amit’s life a living hell. But what happens when Amit hatches a devious scheme to get rich and teach his family a lesson.

name: Hercules
description: Dwayne Johnson delivers an unforgettable performance in the role he was born to play - the mighty Hercules! When a new enemy threatens the innocent, Hercules must lead his fearless team of warriors in a battle against overwhelming odds.

name: Reservoir Dogs
description: When a simple jewelry heist goes horribly wrong, the surviving criminals begin to suspect that one of them is a police informant.

name: The Hottest Summer
description: Each year Lucia volunteers at a Summer Camp in Sicily. This summer however, will be the hottest on record, not just because of the crazy weather, but also because of Nicola, the new soon-to-be-priest deacon who, besides being extremely handsome, hides a tormented and idealistic soul. His arrival sows panic in this seaside community, upsetting Lucia's plans forever.

name: Lord of the Rings: The Two Towers
description: In the part second of the Tolkien trilogy, Frodo Baggins and the other members of the Fellowship continue on their sacred quest to destroy the One Ring--but on separate paths.

name: Double Dhamaal
description: Four idlers make elaborate plans to earn money by investing in buildings but are conned by Kabir, who leaves them unemployed and penniless. Soon, they are on the prowl to avenge their humiliation.

name: Blue Valentine
description: A couple find that they are powerless to stop the downward spiral of their marriage

name: Young Sheldon - Season 4
description: YOUNG SHELDON is a comedy about a young Sheldon Cooper, who finds it isn’t easy growing up in East Texas. Being a once-in-a-generation mind capable of advanced mathematics and science isn’t always helpful in a land where church and football are king. And while the vulnerable, gifted and somewhat naïve Sheldon deals with the world, his very normal family must find a way to deal with him.

name: K.G.F Chapter 2 (Hindi)
description: Vijendra Ingalgi, Son of Anand Ingalgi continues the story of KGF and Rocky in Chapter 2. Rocky survives the attack by Vanaram’s guards after killing Garuda. He is a hero and a saviour to the people of Narachi. While trying to fulfil his promise to his mother, he must face many obstacles in the form of Adheera, Inayat Khalil and Ramika sen.

name: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles: Out Of The Shadows
description: The Turtles are back to battle bigger, badder villains with their new ally Casey Jones. When supervillain Shredder escapes custody with a plan to take over the world, the brothers prepare to take him on but face an even greater threat: the notorious Krang.

name: The Stoneman Murders
description: In 1980s Bombay, a serial killer starts targeting homeless street dwellers, whilst a suspended police officer attempts to solve the case.

name: Tomorrow Never Dies
description: James Bond sets out to stop a media mogul's plan to induce war between China and the UK in order to obtain exclusive global media coverage.

name: Chhota Bheem - The Rise of Kirmada
description: Wicked Kirmada wants to destroy Bheema and Krishna but can gain infinite evil powers only on a full moon night. Meanwhile, Krishna, Bheema and their friends are trying to reunite Raja Indravarma and the neighbouring kings. Will Kirmada become powerful enough to destroy Bheema and Krishna?

name: Katha Kanchiki Manam Intiki
description: Four different types people end up at a grave yard at a certain time. Despite their personal issues, will they come together for justice?

name: The Incredible Hulk
description: Edward Norton leads an all-star cast in this explosive, special effects-packed epic that delivers a mind-blowing final showdown that can only be summed up with one word...INCREDIBLE!

name: Pushpa: The Rise (Hindi)
description: Pushpa Raj (Allu Arjun) a coolie, volunteers to smuggle red sanders, a rare wood that only grows in Andhra, with the help of novel ideas to smuggle the red sanders. Pushpa quickly becomes leader of red sanders smuggling network. While Pushpa is at his prime, a ruthless police officer Bhanwar Singh Shekhawat (Fahadh Faasil) takes charge as SP and ridicules Pushpa for his lineage.

name: The Bourne Supremacy
description: Jason Bourne (Matt Damon) fights back when the CIA tries to kill him.

name: Asuran
description: The son of a farmer from an underprivileged caste kills a rich, upper caste landlord. Will the farmer, a loving father and a pacifist by heart, be able to save his hot-blooded son is the rest of the story.

name: Talaash
description: Inspector Surjan Singh Sekhawat (Aamir Khan) keeps his difficult home life aside and focuses on investigating a mysterious death of a high profile film actor. The investigation leads him to the local red light street, where he meets an alluring sex worker, Rosie(Kareena Kapoor). Rosie helps him to solve the case but still holds lots of hidden secrets. Watch to find out Rosie's deep secrets.

name: Pulp Fiction
description: Three stories intertwine revealing the fate of two hit men, a boxer and couple carrying out a heist.

name: Sherlock: Series 3
description: Sherlock is back, but will things ever be the same again?

name: Warcraft: The Beginning
description: A king, a warrior and a wizard defend the human realm from an invading army of orcs.

name: Don Jon
description: A New Jersey guy dedicated to his family, friends, and church, develops unrealistic expectations from watching porn and works to find happiness and intimacy with his potential true love.

name: Yaar Mera Titliaan Warga
description: Yaar Mera Titliaan Warga is the story of a Couple who, after 6 years of marriage, are bored from each other. To spicy things up, both of them open fake Facebook accounts. But things go sideways when, accidentally, they befriend each other on FB. This "Comedy of Errors" take them on a humorous as well as emotional ride.

name: The Knight of Shadows: Between Yin and Yang
description: Songling (Jackie Chan), a legendary demon hunter, is asked to investigate the mysterious disappearances of young girls from a small village. When he discovers evil forces are kidnapping the girls to feast on their souls, he sets out to save humanity from the inhuman invasion journeying through hidden worlds and colorful dimensions in this fantastical martial arts action-comedy.

name: Hostel Daze - Season 3
description: After experiencing the exhilarating freedom of the initial years and having had their fair share of fun in the past two years; Ankit, Akanksha, Jaat, Jhantoo, Nabomita and Chirag take on the third year, a roller coaster ride of newer awakenings and unique experiences.

name: Navra Maza Navsacha
description: The story is about a women, who realizes that the reason she is childless is due to an unfulfilled promised made by her in-laws to Lord Ganesh. The movie portrays the journey of the couple from Mumbai to Ganapatipule to fulfill the vow.

name: Mortal Engines
description: Peter Jackson presents a world unlike any you've seen. A young woman leads a band of outcasts to stop London, a predator city on wheels, from devouring everything in its path.

name: Alien Convergence
description: A team of disabled service personnel developing a revolutionary thought-controlled fighter plane is pressed into service to repel an alien invasion.

name: The Catcher was a Spy
description: With an ensemble cast, this gripping, espionage thriller brings to life the true story of Moe Berg a World War II spy. His mission: go behind enemy lines in Europe to assassinate the Nazi's chief nuclear scientist before the Germans develop an atomic bomb. Berg must rely on his steel-trap intellect in a high-stakes game of cat and mouse - with the fate of the world hanging in the balance.

name: Pizza 3 The Mummy
description: Nalan dreams of running his restaurant and marrying his love, but is plagued by 2 murders. Kayal, an ambitious app developer, investigates murder and discovers a spirit. Nalan tries to contact the ghost and investigates the previous owner's apartment, where a security man was killed. The story revolves around Nalan is seeking for answer, his next steps and his relationship with the spirit.

name: The Big Bang Theory - Season 5
description: Leonard and Sheldon are brilliant physicists, but none of that genius helps them interact with people, especially women. All this begins to change when a free-spirited beauty, Penny, moves in next door. Sheldon is content spending his nights playing Klingon Boggle with their socially dysfunctional friends. However, Leonard sees in Penny a whole new universe of possibilities ... including love.

name: Mirzapur - Season 1
description: The iron-fisted Akhandanand Tripathi is a millionaire carpet exporter and the mafia don of Mirzapur. His son, Munna, is an unworthy, power hungry heir who will stop at nothing to inherit his father’s legacy. An incident at a wedding procession forces him to cross paths with Ramakant Pandit, an upstanding lawyer, and his sons, Guddu and Bablu.

name: Totally Killer
description: When the infamous "Sweet Sixteen Killer" returns 35 years after his first murder spree to claim another victim, 17-year-old Jamie (Kiernan Shipka) accidentally travels back in time to 1987, determined to stop the killer before he can start.

name: Maanagara Kaaval
description: Vijayakanth is the Assistant Commissioner of Police who arrests Anandraj, a professional killer. But, Nambiar asks to hand over him to Delhi police. Anandraj escapes from Vijayakanth in Delhi and tries to kill Prime Minister Lakshmi. How Vijayakanth saves Lakshmi is the climax of the movie.

name: AIR
description: From award-winning director Ben Affleck, AIR reveals the game-changing partnership between a then undiscovered Michael Jordan and Nike’s fledgling basketball division which revolutionized the world of sports and culture with the Air Jordan brand. Starring Matt Damon, Ben Affleck, Jason Bateman, Chris Messina, Marlon Wayans, Chris Tucker, and Viola Davis.

name: Knuckle Girl
description: An action-packed film by Korean creators, featuring Japanese cast following the story of Ran (Ayaka Miyoshi), who confronts a mysterious organization by participating in a no-rules deathmatch after discovering her missing younger sister Yuzuki (Kotona Minami) is involved in a crime. With danger at every corner, Ran must trade in her boxing gloves for brass knuckles. Will she save her sister?

Arjun Singh Rathod is in love with Lisa, a Christian, but his father wants him to marry a Hindu. He decides to break all ties with his family, both get married, and re-locate to live in a mansion in Palanpur. Shortly Lisa suspects that there is something odd about a particular room in the mansion, Later arjun finds Lisa is possessed by a demonic and seemingly invincible male entity.

name: Fear The Night
description: Follows Iraqi war veteran Tes, as she prepares to strike back after a group of home invaders attack during her sister's bachelorette party, and she discovers that they are hellbent on not leaving any witnesses behind.

name: Scarface
description: A Cuban immigrant cuts a violent path of destruction on his way to the top of Miami's drug trade.

name: Adrift
description: A true story of survival, as a young couple's chance encounter leads them first to love, and then on the adventure of a lifetime as they face one of the most catastrophic hurricanes in recorded history.

name: Saunkan Saunkne
description: Nirmal and Naseeb are happily married couple. Even after 8 years of marriage they don’t have child. On suggestion of her mother-in-law, Naseeb persuades Nirmal to have a second marriage with her younger sister Kirna. Sharing her husband proves to be a difficult task for Naseeb. And this begins the squabbles between the two wives which lead to comic situation.

name: Mirchi
description: When Jay saves a girl from a gang of goons, he develops a special bond of friendship with her. She then falls in love with him and complications arise in their relationship.

name: Sewu Dino
description: In order to finance her father's treatment, Sri works as a maid for the Atmodjo Family. However, she uncovers a dark secret and is compelled to perform a horrifying ritual on Della Atmodjo, a victim of black magic. Sri cannot escape as her life is at stake.

name: T-34
description: In 1944, a courageous group of Russian soldiers managed to escape from German captivity in a half-destroyed legendary T-34 tank. Those were the times of unforgettable bravery, fierce fighting, unbreakable love, and legendary miracles.

name: Catch Me If You Can
description: Frank didn't go to flight school...Frank didn't go to medical school...Frank didn't go to law school...because Frank's still in high school! Inspired by the true story of a brilliant young master of deception and the FBI agent hot on his trail. Directed by Steven Spielberg and starring Leonardo DiCaprio and Tom Hanks. Frank W. Abagnale, Jr. successfully passes himself off as a pilot, a lawyer a...

name: Saathiya
description: "Running away from home can’t keep a couple together. Love can. While for most Love Stories, marriage is the goal, the fact remains -marriage is just the beginning. A story of Aditya (Vivek) and Suhani (Rani Mukerji) SAATHIYA continues from where most love stories end. From the infatuation stage when a couple thinks they are in love right through to when they discover the true meaning of love."

name: BORREGO
description: Our charming heroine (Lucy Hales) is kidnapped & taken captive by an inexperienced drug mule after his ultra-light plane crashes in the desert and forces her out of desperation, to lead the trek across the sweltering desert to his drop. She must fight for her survival while being hunted by the drug cartel.

name: Takeshi's Castle India - Season 1
description: Bhuvan Bam lends his distinctive voice and unique humor as commentator in the brand-new season of Takeshi's Castle. Classic games are making a comeback with new and terrifying obstacles emerging one after another. The lord of the castle, Beat Takeshi, entrusts Bananaman to protect it. Subaru Kimura is the attack force’s new leader. The elite team gathers to bring down the revived Takeshi’s Castle.

name: Rendagam
description: Kichu, an idle guy dreams of making easy money. He is offered an odd job of befriending a strange man called David, who has lost his memory. Will Kichu accept the job? What unleashes next forms the crux of the story.

name: Devi
description: A tale of sisterhood. A tale of suffering. A tale of truth. Who will answer their questions?

name: IIT Krishna Murthy (Accused )
description: Krishnamurthy, an IIT student from Mumbai, travels to Hyderabad to learn about his family. However, when he learns of his uncle's mysterious disappearance, he sets out to find him.

name: The Hurt Locker
description: If war is hell, why do so many men choose to fight? Winner of 6 Oscars in 9 categories The Hurt Locker is an intense portrayal of elite soldiers who have one of the most dangerous jobs in the world: disarming bombs during the Iraq War.

name: The Boy
description: An American nanny is shocked that her new English family's boy is actually a life-sized doll. After she violates a list of strict rules, disturbing events make her believe that the doll is really alive.

name: Big Love
description: Love sparks when Adil, young, full of passion and chasing his dreams meets Adina, a focused and independent woman, making ends meet at a graduate training camp. Adil's love, grand and true, encounters Adina's fears… and that one secret that could destroy everything! Is their love big enough to cover a lie?

name: Yuvarathnaa (Hindi)
description: YUVARATHNAA, revolves around RK University (Govt Aided college) which is at the standpoint of completing 50 glorious years. Gurudev, Principal at RK University, whose life is dedicated for the welfare of the college fights against the privatisation of education system The story entwines between the bond of a teacher and his students.

name: The 40-Year-Old Virgin
description: Three co-workers unite to help their buddy's (Steve Carell) sex life.

name: Archana 31 Not Out
description: A school teacher, who is 28 years old and in in search for a suitable groom!. She has gone through 31 wedding proposals, but not a single one fell into place.

name: Brothers
description: Fate makes two estranged brothers, David (Akshay Kumar) and Monty, (Siddarth Malhotra) clash after years of seeking redemption after their mother's accidental death. While his daughter is David's motivation, Monty, the internet sensation will go to any length for glory. Will this fighter brother duo manage to find peace and make up for their past?

name: Mindcage
description: In this spellbinding thriller, two detectives (Martin Lawrence and Melissa Roxburgh) seek the help of a brilliant serial killer (John Malkovich) when a copycat killer strikes.

name: Uncharted
description: Street-smart thief Nathan Drake (Tom Holland) is recruited by seasoned treasure hunter Victor “Sully” Sullivan (Mark Wahlberg) to recover a fortune lost by Ferdinand Magellan 500 years ago. What starts as a heist job for the duo becomes a globe-trotting, white-knuckle race to reach the prize before the ruthless Moncada (Antonio Banderas), who believes he and his family are the rightful heirs....

name: Permanent Roommates - Season 3
description: Mikesh has the perfect life, whereas Tanya feels stuck. She reckons being stuck in her career is what stops her from being truly happy. Her fix for them to move abroad and Mikesh's resistance to the idea is what leads our Permanent Roommates on a bumpy ride. Eventually, they discover that their love and support for each other surpasses everything else.

name: Beast
description: Idris Elba leads this pulse-pounding thriller about a recently widowed father who goes on vacation to a South African game reserve with his two teenage daughters and suddenly find themselves hunted by a rogue, man-killing lion.

name: Gol Maal
description: Ramprasad works for Bhavani, who discourages his employees from pursuing any hobbies. Things take a hilarious turn when Bhavani catches Ramprasad at a hockey match and he lies about having a twin.

name: Escape Room
description: Six friends test their intelligence when an escape room they participate in takes a dark and twisted turn.

name: The Founder
description: Ray, a salesman, meets the owners of McDonald, a burger joint in Southern California. He realises the potential of the place and decides to make it the biggest restaurant business in the world.

name: Pardes
description: Pardes Is An Award Winning Hindi Romantic Musical Movie, Directed And Produced By Subhash Ghai, Starring Shah Rukh Khan, Mahima Chaudhry, Apurva Agnihotri, Alok Nath, Amrish Puri And Himani Shivpuri In The Lead Roles. Kishorilal Wants An Indian Bride For His NRI Son, He Gets Him Engaged To Ganga, His Friend's Daughter. However, She Seems To Share A Deeper Bond With Arjun, Kishorilal's Foster Son.

name: Maama Maschindra
description: The story traverses around the life of Parasuram. It is about how Parasuram grew up and what kind of hardships he had to go through and how he transformed himself from his fears and inhibitions

name: Campus Beats - Season 3
description: Season 3 sets the stage for the finale for Netra’s story in this chapter where she uncovers the mystery of her past but at a personal cost. This season takes Ishaan Netra love story to a peak. New alliances, mysteries and enemies reveal themselves especially with Rihanna realizing her love for Ishaan. Season 3 Beats celebrates love, friendship, dance and promises the most dramatic season finale.

name: Veeran
description: A 15-year-old boy living in Veeranor, gets struck by lightning and goes into a short coma. After recovery, he gradually realizes that he has superpowers of lightning and mind control. With the help of his powers and demi God "VEERAN" how he handled the villain and avoid the major electirc blast.

name: Agent C I A ( Hindi Dubbed of Dead Drop)
description: Agent C I A is the Hindi Dubbed version of Dead Drop.After surviving a fall from a plane 3000-feet over the ocean, a former CIA operative turned govt contractor re infiltrates a dangerous North Mexican drug trafficking ring to find his own killer.With his memory unraveling,he descends into a murderous rampage while trying to uncover the truth. Who threw him from the plane? Was it his best friend?

name: 007: Road To A Million - Season 1
description: From the producers behind the James Bond movies comes 007: Road To A Million. Nine pairs of everyday people are unleashed on an epic global adventure through a series of Bond inspired challenges, for a shot at winning a life-changing £1,000,000 prize. The Controller (Brian Cox) is the mastermind behind the game, watching the pairs as they hunt for 10 questions he’s hidden around the world.

name: Map of Tiny Perfect Things, The
description: Quick-witted teen Mark (Kyle Allen) is contentedly living the same day in an endless loop when his world is turned upside-down by the mysterious Margaret (Kathryn Newton), also stuck in the same loop. What follows is a love story with a fantastical twist, as the two struggle to figure out how – and whether – to escape their never-ending day.

name: Star vs. Food Survival - Season 1
description: See the thrilling escapades, delicious discoveries and unforgettable dining experiences in the Indian wilderness. Celebrities venture out of their comfort zones and embark on an epic survival adventure to forage unique ingredients to create tasty dishes.

name: Jee Karda- Season 1
description: Seven school friends -who thought that by the time they are 30 their life will be sorted- turn 30 to find that it’s a grand hot mess instead. They live, love, laugh, make mistakes, get their hearts broken, grow up a little but through it all discover that the best of friendships are imperfect and life is a luminous shade of grey.

name: Good Will Hunting
description: A troubled young genius finds his allegiance to his friends challenged by new opportunities.

name: Prema Desam
description: Premadesam is a hyperlinked story, Urban ROM-COM and an Emotional drama. Two Love Stories! Four Lives! Two Problems- One Solution! - One Incident! Did that incident cleared their problems? Or created more difficulties?

name: Hey You
description: The life of an awkward 32 year old software engineer is turned upside down when he finds out the girl he wants to be with is the FANSALONE model he obsesses over and she’s his next-door neighbour.

name: Dhol
description: Four young loafers wish to simplify their life by wooing a loaded heiress. Unfortunately, there's only one rich girl in the neighbourhood. The boys scamper to woo her first, not knowing that their efforts would lead them right into a murder mystery.

name: Kiss of the Dragon
description: Jet Li plays Liu Jiuan, China's top government agent, who arrives in Paris from Shanghai to carry out a sensitive, top-secret mission. Liu is in Paris to assist Richard (Tcheky Karyo), an unorthodox police official with a small army to back him up. The mission goes horribly wrong, as the man Liu had come to help, betrays him.

name: TRIKONA
description: The story of Trikona revolves around Nataraj (Suresh Heblikar), Kodandarama (Achyutha Kumar) and Trivikrama (Rajveer), heading towards Mangalore for different reasons. In between their journey at a remote area of the forest, all 3 cars stuck up with one problem simultaneously. From here the testing time Kaala (Marutesh) begins his play.

name: Juice
description: Manju Singh and her husband are hosting a get-together of families on a warm night. Between the snacks, drinks and the laughs, something unexpected happens.

name: Single Married Divorced
description: Four Lebanese women nearing their 40s face social pressures for being single.

name: The Great Indian Kitchen
description: Like any Indian girl, the bride of the 'The Great Indian Kitchen' moves into her husband's house prepared to adapt to their customs and make it her home. Her husband and his parents do love and care for her. But problems arise when her kind mother-in-law has to be away. She struggles to cope with the mountain of seemingly endless household chores, differences in opinion and unfamiliar traditions.

name: Silsila
description: Amit (Amitabh Bachchan) decides to bury his past life along with his love for Chandni (Rekha) when he meets Shobha (Jaya Bachchan). Shobha's life has come to a standstill after her fiance and Amit’s brother Shekhar (Shashi Kapoor) dies in a crash. When fate brings Amit and Chandni face to face again, both are married to different people - but neither can ignore their feelings for each other.

name: Physics Wallah - Season 1
description: Alakh Pandey is a young, bright and visionary teacher. This is his inspirational journey to create a new age, advanced and highly affordable, parallel education system while fighting the monopolistic, corporate giants and overcoming several internal battles. Find out by watching his inspiring journey only on Amazon miniTV

name: Don
description: This action-thriller is a remake of the well-known hit Don (1978), this time starring Shah Rukh Khan in a double role as Don/Vijay. In a chase to hunt an underworld gangster, DCP D'Silva hires Vijay, a commoner to masquerade as Don, the mastermind of the underworld. But when D'Silva is killed, Vijay himself in a fix as D'Silva was the only man who knew of his true identity.

name: Terror
description: National Award Winning director Satish Kasetty has directed this investigative thriller. Srikanth has played the role of a cop torn between personal and professional issues perfectly. He has a supporting wife  and a father who misunderstands him. Terror breaks a lot of stereotypes in Telugu and stands out as a film that sticks to it's genre. It doesn't bore you despite having a serious story.

name: Pizza 3 The Mummy
description: Nalan dreams of running his restaurant and marrying his love, but is plagued by 2 murders. Kayal, an ambitious app developer, investigates murder and discovers a spirit. Nalan tries to contact the ghost and investigates the previous owner's apartment, where a security man was killed. The story revolves around Nalan is seeking for answer, his next steps and his relationship with the spirit.

name: Hello Meera
description: Hello Meera is a psychological drama

name: Pataakha
description: Based on Charan Singh Pathik's short story Do Behnein, Pataakha narrates the story of two feuding sisters who realize the true nature of their relationship only after marriage separates them.

name: Yatra (Telugu)
description: An Indian politician takes up a decision to go on a 900-mile walking tour as a part of his election campaign. Yatra is an emotional tribute to the former Chief Minister of Andhra Pradesh Y. S. Rajasekhara Reddy.

name: F2 - Fun and Frustration
description: After Venky, Varun also gets married thinking he can keep the wife in control but both of them gets frustrated with the marital life which generates fun.

name: Baba Black Sheep
description: Around a school and will revolve around the happiness, sorrows, joys and notorious activities of children.

name: Your Christmas or Mine 2
description: James’ father had invited Hayley's family to spend Christmas in a luxury ski resort in the Austrian Alps so that they can meet his new American girlfriend. However, after a mix-up at airport, the two families end up at each other’s accommodations on different sides of a valley and opposite ends of the Tripadvisor rating scale. Can Hayley and James’ relationship survive another turbulent Christmas?

name: Watchman
description: A man burdened by his debts decides to steal money from a bungalow to pay off a loan shark. However, he must deal with the dog guarding the door first.

name: Paharganj
description: In Paharganj, Delhi, a woman looks for her lost love and a man deals with his brother's death. Their world is further rocked by a politically motivated murder and a gang war.

name: Siyavar Ram
description: The Legend of Siya Ram is an ancient epic tale which follows Prince Ram's quest to rescue his beloved wife Sita from the clutches of Ravan with the help of an army of monkeys led by the monkey God, Hanuman.

name: Lucifer (Malayalam)
description: A political Godfather, who ruled the God's Own Country, dies and a lot of thieves dressed up as politicians took over the rule. When question arises on the replacement of the 'God', just one name emerges; 'Stephen Nedumbally'.

name: The Haunting
description: Moushmi is accused of killing her best friend and roommate, but claims that she is innocent and a demon made her do it. A psychiatrist and a cop team up to find out if Moushmi is telling the truth. Watch this horror thriller featuring Erica Fernandes, only on Amazon mniTV

name: Somebody I Used To Know
description: On a trip to her hometown, workaholic Ally (Alison Brie) reminisces with her first love Sean (Jay Ellis), and starts to question everything about the person she's become. Things only get more confusing when she meets Sean's fiancé, Cassidy (Kiersey Clemons), who reminds her of the person she used to be.

name: Boonie Bears: Blast Into the Past
description: Boonie Bears: Blast Into The Past Is A Kids Animated Fantasy Film Directed By Leon Ding, Two Bears Get Stuck In The Primitive Age With A Lumberjack They Always Lock Horns With. Later, They Must Save Themselves From Animals In Their Surroundings And Find A Way To Come Back To The Present.

name: Mujhse Shaadi Karogi
description: A hot-tempered young guy named Sameer (Salman Khan) relocates to Goa, where he falls in love with Rani (Priyanka Chopra). However, his new roommate Sunny (Akshay Kumar) starts to behave like a spoke in the wheel with some tricks up his sleeve. Soon Rani starts liking both Sameer and Sunny. Whom will she choose?

name: Ninja
description: A westerner named Casey, studying Ninjutsu in Japan, is asked by the Sensei to return to New York to protect the legendary Yoroi Bitsu, an armored chest that contains the weapons of the last Koga Ninja.

name: I Am Kalam
description: I Am Kalam Is A Award Winning Bollywood Kids Movie, Directed By Nila Madhab Panda. The Film Was Screened At The Cannes Film Festival. It Has Received Many International And National Awards And Honours.  A Poor Boy Derives Inspiration From The Former President Of India, A. P. J. Abdul Kalam. He Then Decides To Change His Name To Kalam And Harbours A Dream Of Meeting The Visionary.

name: Jackie Chan: Kung Fu Master
description: Jackie Chan is the undefeated Kung Fu Master who dishes out the action in traditional Jackie Chan style. When a young boy sets out to learn how to fight from the Master himself, he not only witnesses some spectacular fights, but learns some important life lessons along the way.

name: Sniper Special Ops
description: When the mission to rescue a U.S. Congressman who has been kidnapped by the Taliban goes sideways, Army sniper Jake Chandler and his partner are left behind. Now, on their own, they must survive in enemy territory and wait for their unit to come back for them.

name: Ghoda
description: Ghoda tells the story of a middle class boy's enchantment with the idea of owning a wooden rocking horse, and his father's incredible journey and hardships in trying to make his son's dream come true in a money centric world.

name: Puli (The 19th Century)
description: In the 19th Century, the Maharaja of Travancore seeks the help of a warrior 'Velayudha Chekavar' (Siju Wilson) to counter the noted robber, who steals the valuables belonging to the deity at Anantha Padmanabha Swami Temple. This Period drama with stunning visuals, larger-than-life sets, and a taste of history is a fictitious historical spectacle that offers a perfect cinematic experience.

name: First Act
description: First Act chronicles the journey of child actors and their parents into the Hindi film and TV industry. Through interviews with older child actors, parents, casting directors and filmmakers, the series explores the ecosystem within which children must perform and the challenges they face to achieve the family dream.

name: Nayika Devi: The Warrior Queen
description: Nayika Devi, the Warrior Queen is a Historical drama set in the 12th century. The film is about India's first female warrior.

name: Yuddham Sharanam
description: When his parents' (Rao Ramesh and Revathy) corpses are found in a river under mysterious circumstances, Arjun (Naga Chaitanya) sets out to investigate their deaths. On finding certain disturbing truths, he vows revenge on their killers.

name: Bakasuran (Hindi)
description: A man investigates a disturbing ring of young escorts, cyber harassment and suicide. He knows the importance of parents being aware of their children's problems.

name: Boochamma Boochodu
description: A happily married couple buy a farmhouse but when they enter into it their happiness departs. What's even more dreadful for them is that the demons don't allow them to escape from their clutches.

name: Shiv Shastri Balboa
description: Shiv Shastri, a retiree from India and a big Rocky movie fan moves to the USA and ends up on an unexpected road trip through the American heartland which teaches that it's never too old to reinvent yourself.

name: The Summer I Turned Pretty - Season 2
description: Belly used to count down the days until she could return to Cousins Beach, but with Conrad and Jeremiah fighting over her heart and the return of Susannah's cancer, she's not sure summer will ever be the same. When an unexpected visitor threatens the future of Susannah's beloved house, Belly has to rally the gang to come together—and to decide once and for all where her heart lies.

name: Teen Patti
description: Teen Patti Is An Award Winning Bollywood Crime Thriller Hindi Movie, Directed By Leena Yadav, Starring Amitabh Bachchan, Ben Kingsley, Shraddha Kapoor, R. Madhavan And Raima Sen In The Lead Roles. Perci Trachtenberg, A Great Mathematician, Meets Venkat, A Genius, Who Recounts How His Redefining Theory On Probability Gets Him Embroiled In The Greed And Desperation Of Gambling.

name: Kabul Express
description: Suhel (John Abraham) & Jai (Arshad Warsi) are journalists in search of the Taliban. Imran Khan Afridi (Salman Shahid) - a soldier, needs to escape Afghanistan. Khyber (Hanif Hum Ghum) - an Afghan is as old as the war. Jessica Beckham (Linda Arsenio) - a photojournalist risks her life to photograph the Taliban. Five people from different worlds, their paths are destined to cross in Afghanistan.

name: Area 51
description: Three young conspiracy theorists attempt to uncover the mysteries of Area 51, the government's top secret location rumored to have hosted encounters with alien beings. What they find at this hidden facility exposes horrifying, unimaginable secrets.

name: Much Ado About Nothing
description: Kenneth Branagh brings the William Shakespeare play to life in this 'spirited' (Variety) adaptation of the classic comedy.

name: Black Water: Abyss
description: Five friends exploring a remote cave system in Northern Australia find themselves threatened by a hungry crocodile.

name: Rakta Charitra
description: Rakta Charitra is a 2010 Indian biographical political action thriller based on the life of Paritala Ravindra. The film was directed by Ram Gopal Varma and written by Prashant Pandey. The film starred Vivek Oberoi as Pratap Ravi in the lead role, while Sudeep, Shatrughan Sinha, Abhimanyu Singh, Kota Srinivasa Rao, Sushant Singh, Radhika Apte and Priyamani play supporting roles.

name: Laal Kaptaan
description: In late 18th century Bundelkhand, a bounty hunter wanders in search of a man he has sought for 20 long years. A mysterious young woman obstinately attaches herself to him. Meanwhile, a convoy led by a devious leader makes an arduous journey to the Yamuna, as a prophecy hangs over his infant heir. Somewhere, a ‘junglee’ tracker pieces together a trail as he follows a scent.

name: Padosan | पड़ोसन
description: Bhola has vowed to remain celibate, but when charismatic Bindu moves in next door, he is ready to abandon his pledge. Unfortunately, Bindu’s heart already belongs to her music teacher. Thus, Bhola enlists his musical theatre friends to help him woo the lovely girl-next-door away from him.

name: Panchayat - Season 2
description: With the rise of an opponent against Pradhan Ji, village politics of Phulera heats up. Unable to stay neutral, Abhishek sticks his neck out for Pradhan's family.

name: Aquaman
description: “Aquaman” reveals the origin story of half-human, half-Atlantean Arthur Curry and takes him on the journey of his lifetime-to discover if he is worthy of who he was born to be…a king.

name: Gang Of Ghosts
description: A group of ghosts reside in an old house and live in harmony despite cultural differences. However, when they learn that a builder plans to demolish the building, they come together to stop him.

name: Anything's Possible
description: Anything’s Possible is a delightfully modern Gen Z coming-of-age story that follows Kelsa, a confident high school girl who is trans, as she navigates through senior year. When her classmate Khal gets a crush on her, he musters up the courage to ask her out, despite the drama he knows it could cause. What transpires is a romance that showcases the joy, tenderness, and pain of young love.

name: The Little Things
description: Deputy Sheriff Joe “Deke” Deacon (Washington) is on a search for a serial killer with Sergeant Jim Baxter (Malik), who is unaware that the investigation is dredging up Deke’s past.

name: The Tunnel
description: First responders try to save drivers trapped inside a cold Norwegian tunnel after a tanker truck crashes and catches fire.

name: Saina
description: World Champion. Olympic Medallist. The Doyen Of Indian Badminton. Saina Nehwal Is All Of This And Much More. This Biopic Chronicles The Inspiring Story Of A Gifted Youngster's Ascendance To The Pinnacle Of The Badminton World Through Sheer Passion And Perseverance - A Journey That Has Since Inspired And Empowered An Entire Nation.

name: Baghban
description: An elderly couple wish their children to care for them in their old age. But their children see and treat them as a burden, and they must struggle to regain their worth and dignity to themselves and others.

name: Chhotabheem aur Krishna
description: About 500 years ago, the five kingdoms around Dholakpur joined together to end Kirmada’s rule. Now a mysterious force has brought him back from the dead. The Dholakpur army led by Bheem fight bravely but they is no match to the magically powerful Goblins.

name: Into the Wild
description: After graduating from Emory University in 1992, top student and athlete Christopher McCandless abandons his possessions, gave his entire $24,000 savings account to charity and hitchhiked to Alaska to live in the wilderness.

name: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
description: Based on the comic books.

name: Rubaru
description: Watch Tisca Chopra's Rubaru?, a powerful short where an actress fights against the insurmountable odds to change her fate.

name: Kshamisi Nimma khatheyalli Hanavilla
description: Kshamisi Nimma Katheyalli HaNavilla" means insufficient balance in your account. It takes place in a village backdrop with a universal Concept. Content Oriented Comedy Drama we can say. A Village guy  Shankra who losses 2300 rs because of bank fault and he fights against the bank for this very small but valuable amount makes this concept unique

name: Dr56
description: Priya Krishna (Priyamani), a CBI officer, comes to the City for a murder investigation of a mystery case of three neurosurgeons. Arjun is a theater artist who is suffering from an illness and has to take a pill every 56 minutes.  Priya finds Arjun to be a suspect after going through the CCTV footage. It is quite an enjoyable murder mystery that will find welcome by the faithful of that genre.

name: Up from the Depths: Even More Beasts
description: You’ve met Meg, the ocean’s oldest and most terrifying killer. This time our 85-foot, 100-ton prehistoric predator is joined by a gigantic, ninety-foot, orange tentacled octopus, a pack of ferocious occisorsaurus, part alligator, part velociraptor, equally deadly in both sea and on land, and yes, not just one,

name: 13 Hours: The Secret Soldiers of Benghazi
description: From director Michael Bay, 13 HOURS is the gripping true story of six elite ex-military operators assigned to protect the CIA who fought back against overwhelming odds when terrorists attacked a U.S. diplomatic compound on September 11, 2012.

name: Ravana Lanka
description: Vignesh, along with his friends heads to Goa for vacation, one of them dies in mysterious situations. Others manage to escape, but Krish's girlfriend gets kidnapped. Police officers arrest Krish and the other friends for interrogation. Krish fights back to crack the mystery behind the death of his friends. Twist unfolds when Krish comes to know why the Police arrested them and friends get killed.

name: The Flash Extended Movie Preview
description: Worlds collide in “The Flash” when Barry uses his superpowers to travel back in time, inadvertently altering the future – but will making the ultimate sacrifice be enough to reset the universe?

name: Mane Number 13
description: 5 IT professionals staying together vacate their house due to a situation. They move into a new house were they start facing horrific incidents at night. It terrifies them to death. When they are about to find out what's happening, they are getting killed one after another. Now they have to find out if it's really haunted or someone planning the terror.

name: Nashe Bidu
description: Two delivery agents decide to adopt unlawful methods to make quick money. One of them ends up killing an old lady and lands in trouble.

name: I See You
description: A policeman and his doctor wife (Oscar Winner Helen Hunt) have marriage problems and the son blames the mother. When a 12-year-old boy goes missing, the possible kidnapping looks like some cases from a few years ago. The cold, hard truth about evil in the household is finally uncovered.

name: Parched
description: Parched is a story about women set in the heart of parched rural landscape of Rajasthan, India. It traces the bittersweet tale of four ordinary women Rani, Lajjo, Bijli and Janaki. We see them unapologetically talk about men, sex and life as they struggle with their individual boundaries to face their demons and stage their own personal wars.

name: Beti No.1
description: Beti No. 1 Is A Romantic Comedy Bollywood Hindi Movie, Directed By Rama Rao Tatineni, Starring Govinda, Rambha, Aruna Irani, Johnny Lever, Prem Chopra, Ashok Saraf And  Laxmikant Berde In The Lead Roles. Bharat Youngest Of Three Sons Is Soon Going To Be A Father. When His Wife Gives Birth To A Girl He Is Forced To Switch His Baby With A Male Child Due To His Mother Who Is Very Keen On A Male Heir.

name: Godzilla: King of the Monsters
description: When ancient god-sized monsters rise again, the crypto-zoological agency Monarch faces off against Godzilla, Mothra, Rodan, and King Ghidorah as they all vie for supremacy.

name: Bliss
description: Bliss is a mind-bending love story following Greg (Owen Wilson) who, after recently being divorced and then fired, meets the mysterious Isabel (Salma Hayek), a woman living on the streets and convinced that the polluted, broken world around them is just a computer simulation. Doubtful at first, Greg eventually discovers there may be some truth to Isabel’s wild conspiracy.

name: Your Christmas or Mine?
description: It’s Christmas Eve...Eve. After waving goodbye in Marlyebone Station, new lovers Hayley and James can’t bear to be apart for Christmas, so both decide to surprise each other and unwittingly swap trains by mistake. The snow begins to fall and with it they realise they are trapped with each other’s family for the whole of Christmas. Will their love survive as their secrets get unwrapped?

name: Carnival Row - Season 1
description: With a serial killer loose on Carnival Row, and a government that turns a blind eye to the deaths of its lower class citizens, Rycroft Philostrate, a war-hardened investigator, is the only person willing to stop the murders and maintain the fragile peace. But when Vignette Stonemoss, a faerie refugee, turns up in the Burgue, she forces Philo to reckon with a past he's tried to forget.

name: Gulabo Sitabo
description: Set in present day Lucknow (India), Gulabo Sitabo is a social satire about two impossibly peculiar human beings - Mirza Chunnan Nawab, who stays in a dilapidated mansion and one of the tenants, Baankey Rastogi. The mansion may have seen many dramas unfold over a century of its existence, but still has a final act left as the drama of battle of ownership unfolds, with a priceless lesson to teach.

name: Victoria - Ek Rahasya
description: When Ankita and Siddharth arrive at Hotel Victoria, Scotland, they quickly realise that the creepy owner, Adhiraaj, has more than a few secrets, and Ankita can't help but sense another sinister presence inside the old hotel. Is there a vengeful spirit wandering the hotel, or is it all in their heads? What follows is a race against time as the mystery is unravelled, and nothing is as it seems.

name: Midnight
description: A young deaf woman and her mother battle with a serial killer after they accidentally interrupt one of his kills. A deadly game of cat-and-mouse plays out across the city as the women try to stay one step ahead of their pursuer.

name: Te3n
description: A grandfather, a priest, and a police officer investigate the case of a kidnapped child.

name: Ekkees Tareekh Shubh Muhurat
description: A 55-year-old man named Pandit Girdhari Laal Sharma wants to escape his family legacy of becoming a priest and become a storyteller instead. His dream comes true in an unexpected way, when he is jailed and he finds an audience amongst the prisoners.

name: Humpty Sharma Ki Dulhania
description: Kavya a chirpy, yet fiesty girl from Ambala meets a young, free Delhi lad, Humpty Sharma and they grow close. Her father would never accept her love. Humpty, against all odds, decides to convince Kavya's family to agree to his alliance with her. How he does this forms the rest of the story.

name: Darr
description: DARR is Rahul’s (Shahrukh Khan) story whose love and obsession for Kiran (Juhi Chawla) frees him from all fears of life & death. It is Sunil’s (Sunny Deol) story, whose enduring love & passion for Kiran gives him the courage to face the fear of death. It is Kiran’s story caught between one man’s love & another man’s obsession. She fears one & fears for the other.

name: Nitishastra
description: A sister has to choose between ethics and her family when her brother commits a crime.

name: Chinna Kavundar
description: The village head is a man who sticks to honesty while making judgments. However, when he falls prey to a conspiracy he bravely fights to ensure that justice prevails in his village.

name: Gali Guleiyan
description: In the walled city of Old Delhi, a reclusive shopkeeper spends his days obsessively watching people through hidden closed circuit cameras. When he overhears a boy being beaten, he begins to frantically search for the child. As he becomes lost in the labyrinthine alleys of the city and recesses of his mind, his grasp on reality falters, until he eventually stumbles across a shocking truth.

name: Borat Subsequent Moviefilm
description: Delivery of Prodigious Bribe to American Regime for Make Benefit Once Glorious Nation of Kazakhstan. Two time Academy Award nominee and Golden Globe Winner for Best Motion Picture and Best Actor, Musical or Comedy.

name: Coolie No. 1
description: After being insulted by a rich businessman named Rosario, pandit Jai Kishen teaches him a lesson by getting his daughter married to Raju - a Coolie posing as a millionaire. Soon Raju’s real indentity is exposed but he cooks up a story of having a filthy rich twin. One lie leads to another and things start to go out of hand.

name: Dinoshark
description: A baby dinoshark evolves into a ferocious predatory adult, terrorising tourists and locals offshore from Puerto Vallarta, Mexico.

name: Proximity
description: A young scientist is abducted by extraterrestrials but when no one believes his story he becomes obsessed with finding proof which leads him on a journey of discovery.

name: OK Jaanu
description: Adi and Tara move to Bombay to pursue their dreams. A chance meeting sparks off a heady, no strings attached romance until their careers pull them apart. Will ambition prevail over matters of the heart?

name: Policeodu
description: Police officer Vijay Kumar (Vijay) imposes a self-exile to take care of his daughter Nivi as promised to his deceased wife Mithra (Samantha Ruth Prabhu). When everything seems well, a freak accident lands up Nivi and other children in the backwaters. When Vijay comes to know the reason for the accident, he is forced to take up violence.

name: The Nanny Diaries
description: Unable to decide what to do next after graduating, Annie takes a live-in job as a nanny for the boy of an Upper East Side couple and finds herself juggling with the difficult parents, the challenges of childcare and a new romance.

name: Half Love Half Arranged - Season 1
description: Riya Tanwar finds herself heartbroken after her boyfriend of 3 years dumps her to pursue arranged marriage pursuits. Giving up on conventional dating options, Riya steps into the world of 'arranged dating' only to waddle through a circus of weird matches and an overenthusiastic matchmaker until she finds her Mr. Right.

name: The Aeronauts
description: In 1862, daredevil balloon pilot Amelia Wren (Felicity Jones) teams up with pioneering meteorologist James Glaisher (Eddie Redmayne) to advance human knowledge of the weather and fly higher than anyone in history.

name: Batman Begins
description: Following the death of his parents, Bruce Wayne becomes a masked avenger fighting forces of evil.

name: Munda Southall DA
description: An obligation to keep a family promise separates Arjun and Raavi. Will true love prevail? How will the young lovers find their way back to each other to have a second chance at their perfect love years later?

name: Two Souls
description: Akhil, a troubled young guy attempts suicide, his life changes forever when he had to spend time with a girl he meets in the hospital, both as souls.

name: Anand
description: Anand, a terminally ill man, sets out to live his last days to the fullest. His doctor, Bhaskar, undergoes metamorphosis due to his optimism and decides to write a book on Anand.

name: Ouch
description: What happens when a plan for extra maritial affair goes completely wrong? A man decides to leave his wife for a girl but things take a turn when that girl starts having second thoughts.

name: Predestination
description: For his final assignment, a top temporal agent must pursue the one criminal that has eluded him throughout time. The chase turns into a unique, surprising and mind-bending exploration of love, fate, identity and time travel taboos.

name: Retribution
description: A bank executive receives a bomb threat while driving his children to school that his car will explode if they stop and get out.

name: Digital Village
description: A group of three friends who try their best to spread digital literacy in their village. It is not an easy task for the three men as the villagers stick firmly to their traditional belief system.

name: The Mentalist: The Complete First Season
description: Golden Globe nominee Simon Baker stars as an independent consultant for the California Bureau of Investigation with a remarkable track record for solving crimes using only his razor sharp skills of observation.

name: The Ledge
description: A rock-climbing adventure turns into a living nightmare when a woman captures the murder of her best friend on camera. With nowhere to go, she begins a treacherous ascent up a mountain cliff as the killer and his friends follow close behind.

name: Nani's Gang Leader
description: Gang Leader follows the story of an all-women gang led by Nani who is a crime fiction writer with a pen name 'Pencil'.

name: Rakta Charitra 2
description: The film is a sequel to Rakta Charitra, which was released two months earlier. The film was dubbed in Tamil as Ratha Sarithiram. The film retained much of the cast from the previous film but additionally included Suriya and Priyamani. The film marks the debut of Tamil actor Suriya in the Telugu and Hindi film industries

name: Jo & Jo
description: If you think your family is messed up, wait till you meet the Palathara family! Baby Palathara is a happy go lucky homeo doctor who lives with his wife Lillikutty, daughter Jomol and younger son Jomon. In an interesting turn of events, a love letter finds its way to Palathara home and all hell breaks loos.

name: Tom Clancy's Jack Ryan - Season 1
description: When CIA analyst Jack Ryan stumbles upon a suspicious series of bank transfers his search for answers pulls him from the safety of his desk job and catapults him into a deadly game of cat and mouse throughout Europe and the Middle East, with a rising terrorist figurehead preparing for a massive attack against the US and her allies.

name: L
description: A mother's dream of riding a scooter is not as easy as it seems. Amit Masurkar's 'L' stars Tannishtha Chatterjee, Pankaj Tripathi and Svar Kamble.

name: Kadaram Kondan
description: A trainee doctor has just moved to Malaysia with his pregnant wife. An unidentified man gets admitted in his hospital after an accident who is later identified to be one of the most wanted by the Malaysian police on a murder case. Doctor’s wife is kidnapped with a demand to get the stranger out of the hospital. How the doctor-stranger duo rescue the doctor’s wife is the rest of the movie.

name: Ishaqzaade
description: Rising from the ashes of hooliganism & small town clan wars, comes the love story of a passion ignited by hatred. Of two people. Born to hate. Destined to love. A story… about two fiery bloods played by Arjun Kapoor & Parineeti Chopra, and their fight for power & supremacy. A story about love brewing in the often unrealistic and daunting political confines of rural India. A story called ISHAQZAAD

name: Nikka Zaildar 3
description: The film chronicles the story of Nikka whose father's soul enters his body following his death.

name: The Godfather, Part II
description: The saga of the Corleone crime family continues.

name: Her - Chapter 1
description: After serving a six-month suspension, Archana Prasad is currently working as an ACP with the Telangana State Police. She is commissioned to investigate a murder case, which soon becomes personal.

name: Spider-man
description: While coming to terms with his new-found abilities, Spiderman battles the Green Goblin.

name: The Legend of Tarzan
description: Tarzan, having acclimated to life in London, is called back to his former home in the jungle to investigate the activities at a mining encampment.

name: Custody
description: The movie “Custody” is a run action drama about a normal Constable Siva, Who is assigned to escort a witness from police custody to the courtroom. As a twist in the plot, Siva learns that the entire police department wants the witness dead there starts the real run. When a normal Constable holds the custody of a devil, what will happen in this war? Will the truth prevails?

name: Fury
description: Wardaddy, along with his crew of five members, embarks on a mission that puts many lives in danger. The crew members realise that the odds are against them, but still decide to attack the Nazi army.

name: Once Upon a Time... In Hollywood
description: Actor Rick Dalton gained fame and fortune by starring in a 1950s television Western, but is now struggling to find meaningful work in a Hollywood that he doesn't recognize anymore.

name: Crank
description: Today is the last day of hit man Chev Chelios’ life. He has been given a poison that will kill him if he allows his heart to settle into a normal rhythm. In order to stay alive and take revenge, Chev must keep his adrenaline elevated.

name: Becoming Barbie
description: (Previously Recorded) Showing how Margot Robbie, Greta Gerwig, and team brought Barbie to life.

name: Something From Tiffany's
description: Life – like love – is full of surprises and unexpected gifts. In the holiday romance Something From Tiffany’s, one woman’s life is forever changed by an engagement ring meant for someone else.

name: Julayi
description: Julayi  is a 2012 Indian Telugu-language action comedy film written and directed by Trivikram Srinivas, The film stars Allu Arjun, Ileana D'Cruz, Sonu Sood, Brahmanandam, Kota Srinivasa Rao, Tanikella Bharani, Rao Ramesh and Rajendra Prasad in the lead roles.A thug named Bittu Sonu Sood and a local MLA Varadarajulu Kota Srinivasa Rao plan to rob 15 billion from a bank.

name: The Peripheral - Season 1
description: The Peripheral centers on Flynne Fisher, a woman trying to hold together the pieces of her broken family in a forgotten corner of tomorrow's America. Flynne is smart, ambitious, and doomed. She has no future. Until the future comes calling for her. The Peripheral is master storyteller William Gibson’s dazzling, hallucinatory glimpse into the fate of mankind — and what lies beyond.

name: Tenet
description: Armed with only one word—Tenet—and fighting for the survival of the entire world, the Protagonist journeys through a twilight world of international espionage on a mission that will unfold in something beyond real time.

name: 3 Idiots
description: 3 Idiots Is An Award Winning Bollywood Comedy Movie, Directed By Rajkumar Hirani, Starring Aamir Khan And Kareena Kapoor In The Lead Roles. The Film Won 35 Awards. In College, Farhan And Raju Form A Great Bond With Rancho Due To His Positive And Refreshing Outlook To Life. Years Later, A Bet Gives Them A Chance To Look For Their Long-lost Friend Whose Existence Seems Rather Elusive.

name: Sarkaru Vaari Paata
description: Sarkaru Vaari Paata is a story about Mahi (Mahesh Babu), who believes that financial discipline is a must have quality in everyone. What happens when he encounters Rajendranath who doesn`t respect money. Kalavathi (Keerthy Suresh) is the love interest of Mahi in this action drama.

name: Sarileru Neekevvaru
description: Sarileru Neekevvaru is the story of Ajay Krishna (Mahesh Babu), a superior Army Major who is a player in handling tough tasks across the border. Soon, Ajay moves to Kurnool on a secret mission and he comes to know about a tiff of a family with the antagonist.

name: A Guy Thing
description: A guy wakes up the morning after his bachelor party in bed with another woman---who turns out to be his fiancee's cousin!

name: Takatak
description: Kamakshi and Minakshi are siblings, but their similarities end there. While Kamakshi is level-headed and mature, her younger sister is rather wild and impulsive. With Kamakshi getting hitched to a porn addicted government employee and Minakshi ending up in the middle of a love triangle, the two sisters are about to get caught up in a roller coaster ride of a lifetime.

name: Hulchul
description: A man and woman from feuding families each pretend to fall in love, as part of a revenge plot. Chaos ensues when their fake romance becomes a reality.

name: Mahaveerudu
description: Sathya, a cowardly cartoonist suddenly finds his life narrated by a godly voice, which only he could hear. Everything happens in his life as and how the narrator narrates. Will Sathya overcome his cowardliness to become the Hero, like he actually wrote in the comic book, or will he yield just like he did all his life? This movie is also available as Maaveeran in Tamil and Hindi

name: Babylon
description: A silent film superstar, a young starlet, a production executive, and a musical sensation strive to stay on top of the 1920s Hollywood scene while maintaining relevance in an industry ready to move on to the next best thing.

name: The Outlaws
description: Based on real events, this crime action film depicts a Seoul detective's attempts to keep peace while two Chinese-Korean gangs battle over turf in the neighborhood.

name: Divergent
description: A thrilling action-adventure set in a future where Tris Prior (Shailene Woodley) uncovers a conspiracy by a faction leader (Kate Winslet) that will change society forever.

name: Evaru
description: When a high-ranking police official is killed by his alleged rape victim, Sub-inspector Vikram Vasudev is entrusted with investigating what seems like an open-and-shut case. As he delves deeper, Vikram finds the case spiraling into a dark tale filled with unexpected surprises.

name: Escape Room
description: Six strangers find themselves in circumstances beyond their control and must use their wits to find the clues or die.

name: Naachiyaar
description: Naachiyaar, a film that deals with the unexplored shades of grey in a minor love story; a pregnant young girl and her naive lover who has been accused of rape. An honest and persistent cop, Naachiyaar leads the investigation of the seemingly easy case at first, but what happens when it takes a turn for the worse. How will Naachiyaar as a woman deal with sensitive issues related to the case?

name: Memories
