description: Venki, who is a murder accused.With his memory loss, the lead role is unable to recollect the entire incident of the murder and the rest of the story is about how he gets out

name: Fraud Saiyaan
description: Fraud Saiyyan is the story of a con artist in North India who convinces women to marry him just so he can live off their money.

name: Nam Naani Maduve Prasanga
description: Naani s strange predicament is that he is not married because he is an agriculturist. A rib tickling comedy of errors ensues as the story proceeds .

name: Khubsoorat
description: Nirmala Gupta runs her household and family in a very strict and authoritarian manner. While most of her family resent this, they do obey her and carry out her instructions, so as to be on her good side. Things start to change after her second son gets married to Anju. Manju, Anju's sister, comes over to stay for a few days with the Gupta family, and is accepted by everyone except Nirmala.

name: Gods Of Egypt (Hindi)
description: In this Hollywood / English dubbed movie, Gerard Butler and Nikolaj Coster-Waldau star as rival gods locked in an epic battle to decide the fate of the universe in this thrilling fantasy-adventure.

name: Four More Shots Please! - Season 3
description: A sad goodbye, some giggles, some tears and a heavy heart. That's how we see the four girls this season. Each of them is saddled by baggage, most of which slump their shoulders and almost make them fall. All that the four of them are seeking this season is closure but sometimes the closing chapters are the most painful ones.

name: Anbanavan Asaradhavan Adangadhavan
description: Michael, a criminal leader, gives up a life of crime and settles in Chennai under a different name. He soon falls in love with a woman but learns that she wants to marry a man who looks just like him.

name: The Cutting Edge
description: Action and romance take to the screen when a self-centered ex-hockey star (D.B. Sweeney) and a prima donna champion figure skater (Moira Kelly) become unlikely partners in pursuit of Olympic gold.

name: Flashbacks of a Fool
description: Joe Scott (Daniel Craig) is a washed up Hollywood star, whose hedonistic lifestyle of sex, drugs, and celebrity has taken its toll. Handsome even in his drug-addled 40s, he leads a directionless, lonely life in his opulent Malibu mansion. Only when confronted by tragedy is he forced to face up to the ghosts of his past.

name: Ki & Ka
description: Kia is driven, while Kabir prefers being a househusband. Kabir gains fame from interviews about their unconventional marriage, causing tension with Kia. After Kia's mother is hospitalized, she apologizes for her jealousy. The couple reconciles, and Kia becomes CEO of Kabir's father's company.

name: Yeh Jawaani Hai Deewani
description: For Bunny travelling is love, travelling is life. While Naina is a geek, looking for a stable career. Naina meets Bunny and his friends on a trekking trip. Bunny's zeal for life helps her discover a new and confident self. She hopelessly falls in love with Bunny. Bunny loves her too but loves travelling more. Will Bunny choose a 'happily ever after' with Naina or adventure? Watch to find out!

name: Jaspreet Singh: Koi Load Nahi
description: Jaspreet Singh takes on "mundane" topics like the ever-growing motivation market, godmen, serious parenting to the "tough" bouncers like his door bell, the salad he made and the absurdity of the teenage. His first comedy special is a perfect amalgamation of his niche observations, signature laid back attitude with quick paced punchlines.

name: Platoon
description: Inspired by Oliver Stone's own experiences, this anti-war epic tells the tale of PFC Chris Taylor (Charlie Sheen), an Army recruit sent to Vietnam, who witnesses the atrocities of war – many of which are carried out by his comrades.

name: Thoda Pyaar Thoda Magic
description: In a rare court verdict, business tycoon Ranbeer (Saif Ali Khan) is sentenced to raise the very children whose parents he killed in an accident. The orphans hate him and want revenge. When Ranbeer and the children pray for divine intervention, The Big Man above sends Geeta (Rani Mukerji) - a mischievous, childlike, lovable angel to the rescue, with a mission to bring Ranbeer and the kids together.

name: Get a Job
description: Miles Teller, Anna Kendrick, and Bryan Cranston lead this all-star comedy about the hilarious attempts of a recent college grad, his girlfriend, and their friends to find work.

name: Dia
description: Dia tells the story of a young, introvert girl whose routine life brightens up when she falls for Rohith, one of her fellow college mates. Being an introvert girl and trying to express her love becomes the biggest challenge of her life.

name: New Bandits - Season 1
description: Adrift and desperately needing money to pay for his ailing adoptive father's care, Ubaldo, a bank clerk who's unable to remember his childhood, receives an inheritance that will change his destiny for good. He goes to Cratará, in the heart of the northwest desert, where he'll become the leader of a pack of ruthless bandits, fulfilling the legacy of his biological father - a mythical cangaceiro.

name: Asambhav
description: Asambhav Is A Bollywood Action Thriller Hindi Movie, Directed By Rajiv Rai, Starring Arjun Rampal, Priyanka Chopra, Naseeruddin Shah, Dipannita Sharma, Tom Alter And Milind Gunaji In The Lead Roles. Army Officer Adit Is Sent Undercover To Switzerland To Save The Kidnapped President Of India. On The Way, He Meets Alisha, A Singer, And Together They Fight Against A Web Of Lies They Are Trapped In.

name: Maatr
description: A politician's son and his friends kidnap and sexually assault a school teacher and her daughter. After her daughter dies in the incident, the woman decides to take revenge.

name: Crushed - Season 3
description: Our favourite gang at Lucknow Central Convent School is done with their board examinations, and Father Lawrence offers 40 students of 11th and 12th standard to apply on a first-come, first-served basis for an exchange programme- Young Tarang, at Don Roberts School, Dehradun, during their summer holidays. Aadhya is unusually excited to hear the same and convinces her unsure friends about the trip.

name: Mamma Mia! The Movie
description: A bride secretly invites three men from her mother's (Meryl Streep) past to come to the wedding.

name: Amir Garib
description: Moni leads a dual life as a musician by the day and a vigilante at night who robs from unscrupulous traders and distributes their wealth amongst the poor. Problem arises when he's unmasked.

name: Breaking Surface
description: During a winter dive on a remote part of the coast in Northern Norway, a rockfall traps a girl to the ocean floor. Will her sister save her?

name: Maayavan ( In Hindi )
description: Maayavan' is a Bollywood Sci-Fi crime thriller in Hindi (dubbed from Tamil movie: Maayavan). Kumaran is a cop on duty who witnesses a murder committed by Dheena and gives chase and almost loses his life but luckily escapes after killing him. and the investigation leads to a shocking revelation that could almost shake the entire world.

name: Karumegangal Kalaigindrana
description: Two fathers from distinct age brackets and social backgrounds attempt to reunite with their daughters.

name: Carry On Balle Balle
description: Jass, an orphan, dreams of settling down in Canada but is not eligible to immigrate. He decides to marry an NRI girl, Meet, to fulfil his dream.

name: Bhaag Saale
description: A smart young chap knots into a big trouble: he must defy a big time goon, to retrieve something priceless and regain his love.

name: Murder In Agonda - Season 1
description: A quiet villa in a scenic village of Goa, Agonda but a murder changes everything! Secrets, mysteries, plotting, heart-breaks and chaos, everything will unleash. Will the culprit be caught or will innocents suffer, available only on Amazon miniTV

name: Sitting In Bars With Cake
description: Inspired by true events, Sitting in Bars with Cake follows two best friends in their 20s navigating life in L.A. Extrovert Corinne convinces Jane, a shy, talented baker, to commit to a year of bringing cakes to bars, to help her meet people and build confidence. But when Corinne receives a life-altering diagnosis, the pair faces a challenge unlike anything they’ve experienced before.

name: The Legend of Muay Thai: 9 Satra
description: "9 Satra" is an animated action fantasy which follows the adventures of young man name Ott, whose destiny is to save his home-land of Ramathep from the devil power of Dehayaksa. Legend says that only one man that can use Ramthep's most ancient weapon, a mythical stone that represents the spirit of Muay Thai.

name: Hostel Daze - Season 2
description: 6 friends enter their second year of college and dig deeper into the notorious universe of an Indian hostel. Hostel Daze Season 2 incorporates the second chapter of hostel-life in the lives of Ankit, Jaat, Chirag, Jhantoo, Akanksha and Nabomita. The problems, the hurdles and the unlimited quirks have now doubled.

name: The Big Bang Theory - Season 10
description: Leonard and Sheldon are brilliant physicists—geniuses in the laboratory, but socially challenged everywhere else. Despite their on-again, off-again relationship in the past, Leonard and Penny have finally gotten married. Even Sheldon has found a female companion, entering into a "Relationship Agreement" with neurobiologist Amy Farrah Fowler.

name: The Childe
description: The Childe focuses on a man born to a Korean father and a Filipino mother who aspires to be a boxer. He travels to the Philippines in the hopes of tracking down his father and in the process he gets mixed up with some bad people.

name: Mei
description: The story begins with a young girl who goes missing and medical crimes happen. The rest of the story is about how the missing girl and the medical racket case gets linked and how the police solves the case.

name: Mumbai Varanasi Express
description: Life is much more than the satisfaction we draw out of material things. Watch out for the difficult choice to be made.

name: Two Night Stand
description: An online hook-up turns into something more after a snowstorm traps two lovers (Miles Teller, Analeigh Tipton) in one's New York apartment.

name: MCA (Middle Class Abbayi)
description: Nani(Nani) a middle-class guy who stays with his sister in law(Bhumika). He leads a happy go lucky life with his girlfriend(Sai Pallavi) but things change all of a sudden when Bhumika who is a government servant lands into problems with a dreaded criminal(Naresh Vijay) in Warangal. Rest of the story is as to how a simple guy like Nani confronts the dreaded gangster and saves his sister in law.

name: Roja
description: Roja Is An International And National Award Winning Tamil Film Directed By Mani Ratnam,Starring Arvind Swamy In The Lead Role And Music By A. R. Rahman.It Garnered 11 Awards From 13 Nominations.Roja Is A Story Of A Simple Girl From A Village In Tamil Nadu Who Makes Desperate Efforts To Find Her Husband Rishi After He Is Kidnapped By Militants During A Secret Undercover Mission In Jammu And Kashmir

name: On a Wing and a Prayer
description: In this extraordinary true story of faith and survival, ON A WING AND A PRAYER follows passenger Doug White’s (Dennis Quaid) harrowing journey to safely land a plane and save his entire family from insurmountable danger, after their pilot dies unexpectedly mid-flight.

name: Action
description: An Indian army officer goes after the mastermind behind a terror attack that also resulted in a personal loss to him.

name: Raththam
description: Ranjith, an acclaimed editor of a leading publication leaves the job when he loses his wife and lives a secluded life in Kolkata with his daughter. After a few years, when his close friend is killed by a fanatic fan, Ranjith is forced to get back to the job.

name: Thank You
description: Abhi is a successful entrepreneur who calls himself ‘self-made’ and doesn’t believe anyone but himself is the reason for his success. But when he’s forced to look back on life, what does he realise?

name: Kheer
description: As we age, life can get lonelier and the definition of relationships, mature. 'Kheer' is a delightful serving of love and companionship where secrets get accidentally spilt and shared.

name: The Roundup
description: Followed by Ma Seok-do, who heads to a foreign country to extradite a suspect. However, he discovers additional murder cases and learns about a killer who had committed crimes against tourists for many years.

name: Varisu
description: Vijay, the prodigal son of business tycoon Rajendran agrees to take over the reins of the business, much to the chagrin of his brothers. But can Vijay prove himself to be a worthy varisu and also reunite his now-broken family? This movie is also available as Vaarasudu (Telugu), Vamshajan (Malayalam) and Vaarasdara (Kannada)

name: Sabse Bada Don
description: 'Don'  Seenu (Ravi Teja) since childhood due to the strong influence of the Amitabh Bachchan's 'Don'. He joins with Machiraju (Sayaji) whose rival to Narsing (Srihari). Machiraju gives Seenu a task, to win the heart of Narsing's sister. But, he wins the heart of Deepthi (Shriya) and later, he discovers a twist which leads to various turns in the story. What happens next is the essence.

name: Dinosaurs
description: The film revolves around two rival gangster families vying for control of the city. Their ongoing feud forms the core conflict of the story, driving the plot forward with escalating tension and deadly consequences.

name: Lady Macbeth
description: An excellent and sophisticated tale of revenge and passion. Rural England, 1865. Stifled by a loveless marriage to a bitter man twice her age, Katherine has to live with a cold and unforgiving family. When she embarks on a passionate affair with a young worker on her husband's estate, a force is unleashed inside her, so powerful that she will stop at nothing to get what she wants.

name: Jamba Lakidi Pamba
description: Varun (Srinivas Reddy) and Pallavi (Siddhi Idnani) are in love and get married without the consent of their parents. Insecurities and ego problems arise and creates trouble in paradise within a year. They meet a ruthless lawyer (Posani Krishna Murali) and file for divorce. Under strange circumstances, their souls get interchanged. What happens after that is forms the story of hilarious drama.

name: Texas Chainsaw Massacre
description: A young woman travels to Texas to collect an inheritance; little does she know that an encounter with a chainsaw-wielding killer is part of the reward.

name: Baazigar
description: A young man with a vendetta against a business tycoon seduces and kills his eldest daughter and then proceeds to his younger daughter but she begins to suspect her new lover's ulterior motive.

name: O-O-O-No Shinnosuke
description: A spin-off anime created in celebration of Shin chan's 25th anniversary of its TV series. The 4 series have unique settings and unimaginable storylines that go beyond the Nohara Family’s daily life. A thriller suspense in outer space? A dark fantasy with monsters and toys? Not only fans of Shin chan, but first-timers and adults are sure to laugh and enjoy this “Upscaled” Shin chan series.

name: Hasee Toh Phasee
description: An Indian romantic comedy about Nikhil (Sidharth Malhotra) who is very committed to his girlfriend Karishma (Adah Sharma), falls in love with her younger sister Meeta (Parineeti Chopra) but is too guilty to follow his heart. Whom will he choose ?

name: Thugs Of Hindostan (Hindi)
description: A story about one man’s love for his nation and another’s love for power. An epic adventure filled with edge-of-the-seat thrills and war on the seas.

name: Pushpa: The Rise (Telugu)
description: Pushpa Raj (Allu Arjun) a coolie, volunteers to smuggle red sanders, a rare wood that only grows in Andhra, with the help of novel ideas to smuggle the red sanders. Pushpa quickly becomes leader of red sanders smuggling network. While Pushpa is at his prime, a ruthless police officer Bhanwar Singh Shekhawat (Fahadh Faasil) takes charge as SP and ridicules Pushpa for his lineage.

name: Hanuman the Immortal - 2
description: Thousands of years after the war of Lanka, a mutant demon warrior is back with a vengeance. Resurrected after the apocalyptic war, this dark force Raaka, has set his eyes on what all human eyes have failed to see, the hidden land of the Vaanars and his nemesis, Hanuman! He is the only hurdle en-route the evil enterprise of reawakening the Asura race. Watch this thrilling story unfold.

name: Buhe Bariyan
description: In a Punjab village, Bhooro leads a self-reliant group fighting social issues. Tensions rise as women challenge traditional norms, making men uneasy

name: Battle On Buka Street
description: The plot revolves around the battle between two women who confront each other in a food challenge in order to win the prestigious 'King of Buka Street' which is a title conferred to the best local food seller in the region.

name: My Fault
description: Noah must leave her town, boyfriend and friends to move into her mom's new husband's mansion. There, she meets her new stepbrother Nick and their personalities clash from the very beginning. But the attraction they feel will lead them to live a forbidden relationship, where their rebellious and tormented tempers will turn their worlds upside down, making them fall madly in love.

name: 72 Hours: Martyr Who Never Died
description: India was ill-prepared with the 1962 Sino-Indian War. Jaswant's paltan (platoon) is sent to defend from the encroaching Chinese army from the northeastern front. Due to adverse circumstances and setbacks, the infantry has to step back. However, Rifleman Jaswant Singh Rawat refuses to leave and fights against the Chinese army alone for 72 hours.

name: 2 Broke Girls: The Complete Third Season
description: One of television’s top comedies continues for a third sensational season as sarcastic Max and sophisticated Caroline, new best friends who met waitressing at the same Brooklyn diner — try to get their cupcake business further off the ground. At the end of season two, the girls discovered a hidden room in the diner — perfect to operate Max’s Homemade Cupcakes out of.

name: The Enforcer
description: Sex slavery combined with technology where the abuse of its prisoners is streamed online to an anonymous audience on the dark web. An Enforcer has to sacrifice everything to save a young girl he has befriended from his femme fatale boss who is involved in cybersex trafficking. Miami. Under the glitz and glam, fast cars and neon dreams, there's a dark underbelly.

name: Ujda Chaman
description: Ujda Chaman is about a 30 -year-old bachelor Chaman Kohli, a Hindi lecturer with Premature Balding & in quest of a beautiful wife. After facing several rejections as a prospective groom because of his baldness, Chaman hits rock bottom when an astrologer gives him a deadline to find himself a wife or remain a celibate forever.

name: Source Code
description: A soldier (Jake Gyllenhaal) wakes up in someone else's body and discovers he's part of an experimental government program to find the bomber of a commuter train within 8 minutes.

name: The Family Man - Season 1 (Available in Hindi, English, Telugu & Tamil)
description: The Family Man is an edgy action-drama series, which tells the story of a middle-class man who works for a special cell of the National Investigation Agency. While he tries to protect the nation from terrorists, he also has to protect his family from the impact of his secretive, high-pressure, and low paying job.

name: Rings
description: In the third installment of the 'The Ring' franchise, young Julia watches a copy of the cursed video to save her boyfriend Holt. But Julia makes a terrifying discovery: the new copy has images no one has ever seen before.

name: The Twilight Saga: New Moon (Hindi)
description: In this Hollywood / English dubbed movie, the second film in the Twilight franchise. Separated from Edward, Bella begins a friendship with werewolf Jacob Black (Taylor Lautner) that leads her even deeper into the supernatural.

name: Venom: Let There Be Carnage
description: Venom battles the evil Carnage.

name: Zid
description: A journalist, who is still struggling to put his past behind, learns that his landlords daughter, a psychopath, is madly in love with him.

name: Suits #04 (2013/14)
description: Picked up for a fourth season, USA's top-rated and critically-acclaimed drama series "Suits". The series stars Gabriel Macht ("Love and Other Drugs"), SAG Award nominee Patrick J. Adams ("Luck"), Gina Torres ("Firefly"), Rick Hoffman ("Samantha Who"), Meghan Markle ("CSI: Miami") and Sarah Rafferty ("Brothers & Sisters").

name: Saaho (Tamil)
description: After many innocents become scapegoats in a mind boggling robbery, an undercover super cop is summoned to the city. While the investigation progresses, dark secrets about one of the biggest mafias of the world surfaces but with a bundle of mysteries attached.

name: Legends of the Ramayana with Amish - Season 1
description: Acclaimed author Amish Tripathi traverses 5,000 kilometers in the footsteps of Rama, India's biggest cultural hero. He travels to key locations, mapping myth with geology, customs and belief to bring the legends of Rama's travels alive.

name: Baap Manus
description: Amidst the heartache of losing his beloved wife on the day of his daughter's birth, a single father sets out to deal with his doubts and fears about becoming a perfect father.

name: Aitraaz
description: Aitraaz Is An Award Winning Romantic Thriller Hindi Movie, Directed By Abbas Mustan And Produced By Subhash Ghai, Starring Akshay Kumar, Priyanka Chopra, Kareena Kapoor, Amrish Puri, Paresh Rawal And Annu Kapoor. Raj, A Married Man, Is Falsely Accused Of Rape By His Ex Girlfriend Who Is Also His Employer's Wife. This Motivates Him To Sue Her For Sexual Harassment Despite Societal Pressures.

name: War of the Worlds
description: A contemporary retelling of H.G. Wells‘ classic, the sci-fi thriller reveals the extraordinary battle for the future of humankind through the eyes of one American family.

name: The Adventures Of Lleo - Season 1
description: The most loved character from permanent roommates, LLEO aka laxman laal ebote gets accidentally rich because some Nigerian prince sent him 500million dollars. He is living an opulent life. But he gets cheated while playing a game as he clicks on a donation link and his entire property get seized. Now the adventure begins as he is homeless and meets purushottam the cab driver on road.

name: HAYWIRE
description: From Academy Award-winning director Steven Soderbergh of Ocean's 11, 12 & 13 comes HAYWIRE. A Female Assassin covert operative is hired to various global missions to perform jobs which governments can't authorize. When the operation goes awry, she needs to use all of her skills & tricks to escape an international manhunt and eliminate the last remaining link of the conspiracy against her.

name: Inji Iduppazhagi
description: Soundarya aka Sweety (Anushka Shetty) is overweight yet confident woman who joins a slimming centre to attract Abhishek (Arya). When she discovers the unhealthy practices the slimming centre uses to speed up the weight loss, she decides to expose it to the world.

name: New York
description: NEW YORK is a contemporary story of 3 young friends (John Abraham, Katrina Kaif and Neil Nitin Mukesh) set against the larger than life backdrop of NYC, whose beautiful lives are turned upside down by the larger event of 9/11. Enter Agent Roshan (Irrfan), a FBI undercover agent who sets the ball rolling for a set of events that turn the lives of these friends into a thrilling roller coaster ride.

name: Ranga Maarthaanda
description: Raghava Rao (Prakash Raj), a celebrated theatre artiste who has ruled the stage for decades, decides to retire on a high to spend time with his family. While his intentions are pure, he struggles to come to grips with the new reality changing landscape, selfcentred family members and his glory days from the stage now behind him. Will he be able to play different characters that life throws at him?

name: Single Shankarum Smartphone Simranum
description: A frustrated food delivery boy gets a super intelligent AI phone which has all the emotions of a girl. It changes his life completely when it starts falling in love with him

name: Saare Jahaan Se Mehnga
description: A man under pressure due to the countrys growing inflation rates comes up with a unique idea to deal with the rising prices. However, things go wrong and his naivety lands him in big trouble.

name: Hi Venus (Hindi) - Season 1
description: The story follows Ye Shi Lan (Liang Jie), a pediatrician working in a remote village as a part of a social welfare program. She has been waiting for her notice to return to An Xing Hospital. One day, Shi Lan has an unusual encounter with Lu Zhao Xi (Joseph Zeng), the newly elected CEO of An Xing Hospital.

name: Game Of Death (English Dubbed)
description: Bruce Lee's last screen work, "Game of Death" is a film that mystifies the man & the legend. Lee plays Billy, a successful movie star, who is shot for refusing to join an international syndicate. He fakes his own death as an opportunity to pursue the gang in secret. Although his death inevitably affected the final production of the film, it still contains some most unforgettable sequences.

name: Kavalai Vendam
description: Arvind Baskar (Jiiva) and Divya (Kajal Aggarwal) are friends from their childhood days. They get married when they grow up. But on their wedding night, Divya fights with Arvind and walks out. After 3 years, Divya gets engaged to Arjun (Bobby Simha) and to break her relationship legally with Arvind, she seeks divorce from him. What happens from there is the rest of the movie.

name: The People We Hate At The Wedding
description: In this hilariously raunchy comedy, dysfunctional American siblings Alice (Kristen Bell) and Paul (Ben Platt) along with their ever-optimistic mom (Allison Janney), are invited to the British wedding of their estranged half-sister Eloise (Cynthia Addai-Robinson) as a chance for them to reconnect as – more or less – adults, and learn to love each other like they once did

name: Marlowe
description: Detective Phillip Marlowe becomes embroiled in an investigation with a wealthy family in Bay City, California, after a beautiful blonde hires him to find her former lover.

name: Modern Love Mumbai – Season 1
description: Modern Love Mumbai explores 6 unique yet universal stories of human connection and love in its varied forms – romantic, platonic, parental, sexual, familial, marital, self love. Inspired by the beloved New York Times column, this edition of the hugely popular original version of the same name, explores love in all of its complicated and beautiful forms against the city of dreams, Mumbai.

name: About Fate
description: This romantic comedy is a tale of two strangers who believe in love, but seem to never be able to find its true meaning. In a wild twist of events, fate puts each in the other's path one stormy New Year's Eve, and comedy and chaos ensue.

name: 32 Malasana Street
description: A family moves to a new house to live the dream of the big city. A house where dreams turn into nightmares.

name: The Last King
description: In the year 1206 Norway is raged by civil war. The King's illegitimate infant son, Håkon Håkonsson, which half the kingdom wants killed off, is guarded in secrecy by two men. A story which changed the course of the country's history.

name: The Bone Snatcher
description: Alex is a scientist who works for a firm that monitors the safety of people traveling in dangerous environments. He's dispatched to Namibia on an assignment, and soon finds himself thrown in with eccentric locals who are searching for diamonds. When four of the jewel hunters are found dead in the desert with the flesh stripped from their bodies, it's up to Alex to find out what's gone wrong.

name: Ragini Mms
description: Ragini MMS is a sensual paranormal film, where a couple's weekend getaway turns eerie when they discover hidden cameras capturing something metaphysical. Captured by an inexplicable force, they face terrifying experiences. An exciting blend of fact and fiction

name: Ulavuthurai
description: Ulavuthurai is a 1998 Tamil action film directed by Ramesh Selvan. The film features Vijayakanth, Meena and Sanghavi in lead roles, Several people die mysteriously in the sea, so the navy looks for its best officer Vasanth Periyasamy (Vijayakanth) to investigate the case. Vasanth Periyasamy changes his identity into Krishnamoorthy. He is now a car driver and lives in disguise for his family's sake

name: My Love Puppy
description: My Love Puppy is about a man who is about to get married going through an adventure when he sets off with his friend to drop his dog at the pet sitters.

name: Kantara - A Legend
description: Kantara is a story set in the fictional village of Dakshina Kannada which explores the ideological conflict of human and nature. A battle of ego swirls along tradition and culture of the land. Will Shiva, the protagonist of the film be able to reinstate peace and harmony in the village perceiving his existence?

name: Mohra
description: Mohra Is An Bollywood Action Thriller Hindi Movie, Directed By Rajiv Rai, Starring Akshay Kumar, Sunil Shetty, Raveena Tandon, Naseeruddin Shah, Gulshan Grover, Paresh Rawal And Kulbhushan Kharbanda In The Lead Roles. Journalist Roma And Her Boss Jindal Free Vishal From Jail After He Comes To Her Aide. He, However, Realizes That He Is Being Used As A Pawn After He Starts Working For Jindal.

name: Bengaluru Boys
description: This feature film is a very trendy urban culture movie targeting Bangalore youth, that will keep audiences off all ages engaged. It has a wonderful star cast of talented performers, and a blend of youthful fresh talented movie crew working hard behind the screens to make the movie a Super Hit under an established movie production banner.

name: Villain
description: Villain is a 2020 British action crime drama film directed by Philip Barantini and starring Craig Fairbrass. Based on Eddie Franks is a former criminal who attempts to help his family by reconnecting with his daughter and clearing his brother's debt. Despite his efforts, he is drawn back into a criminal way of life, with devastating consequences.

name: Son Of India
description: Son of India is the story of a seasoned politician, who turns into a serial killer after bailed from the Jail. What are the reasons behind his killing spree is the rest of the story.

name: Udeekan Teriyan
description: Sukhi's wife has been missing for months, causing him sleepless nights and intense loneliness. While trying to find his wife, Sukhi meets Amrita, who also happens to be searching for her missing husband. Now only time can tell what is in store for them.

name: Beauty and the Beast
description: An unexpected romance blooms after the the youngest daughter of a merchant who has fallen on hard times offers herself to the mysterious beast to which her father has become indebted. Armed with her courage, ignoring every danger and opening her heart, Beauty manages to release the Beast from his curse. And in doing so, she discovers true love.

name: Dandupalya 2
description: The story continues from where it was ended in the first part. As the entire gang from Dandu Palayam is prosecuted and 80 murder cases are registered on them, they get a death sentence

name: At First Sight
description: Val Kilmer and Mira Sorvino star in the amazing true story of a visually-impaired man, restored by the miracle of science and the wonder of love.

name: Padi Padi Leche Manasu
description: Set in Kolkata, the romantic drama chronicles the shared destiny of a young couple as they navigate through the highs and lows of a budding relationship.

name: The Cabin in the Woods
description: Bad things happen when five friends go to a remote woodland cabin.

name: Kung Fu Panda 3
description: Po trains a village of pandas to fight a supernatural enemy.

name: Aickarakkonathe Bhishaguaranmaar
description: The movie  follows the story of Ayurvedic physician Sukumaran Vaidyar and his family, who run a charitable ayurvedic resort named Ayur Home. Despite the presence of a multi-specialty hospital in the area, the villagers of Aickarakkonam believe in the efficacy of Ayur Home. The film recounts certain events that unfold in the life of Sukumaran Vaidyar, and how it affects the village and its people.

name: Hum Saath-Saath Hain
description: Hum Saath-Saath Hain is a classic yesteryear film which speaks about family values. Ramkishen and Mamta have three sons, Vivek, Prem and Vinod. As Vivek is Mamta's stepson, she embitters her heart towards him for the sake of her own sons and Vivek dutifully accepts her decision.

name: Saroj Ka Rishta
description: To win the love of her childhood sweetheart Vikram and to get rid of her obesity, Saroj decides to undergo a body transformation. However, things take a turn when Vikram lands up in Ghaziabad from Canada, unannounced.

name: Harlan Coben's Shelter - Season 1
description: Based on the bestselling series by Harlan Coben, Shelter follows the story of Mickey Bolitar after the death of his father leads him to start a new life in suburban New Jersey. When another new student disappears, Mickey finds himself tangled in a web of secrets. With the help of two new friends, Spoon and Ema, they reveal a dark underground that may hold the answers to decades of disappearances.

name: Yatri Kripya Dhyan De
description: Sumit, a traveler in his early 30's meets a hitchhiker while driving in the hills. They get talking and what unfolds later is a series of horror filled and surprising turns.

name: Varisu (Hindi)
description: Vijay Rajendran is a happy to go lucky man. Things change when his father becomes terminally ill, and he is left to manage his business empire.

name: Great White
description: When a seaplane is destroyed in a freak accident, five people find themselves drifting on a raft. At the mercy of the tide and with no hope of rescue, the helpless situation takes a horrifying turn when they are terrorized by a ravenous great white.

name: O Kadhal Kanmani
description: Two young lovers are compatible in every way - they even agree that marriage is futile. However, their emotions are not so easily managed, especially when they witness the unconditional love of the older couple with whom they live

name: Under The Dome - Season 01
description: UNDER THE DOME, a 13-episode serialized drama from Amblin Television based on Stephen King's best-selling novel, is the story of a small town that is suddenly and inexplicably sealed off from the rest of the world by an enormous transparent dome.

name: About Adam
description: When carefree Lucy (Kate Hudson) finally meets her perfect man, Adam (Stuart Townsend), she's ready to give up her wild ways and settle down for good. But while Lucy is busy making plans for her wedding, Adam is busy charming the rest of her family!

name: Panchayat - Season 1
description: Panchayat is a comedy-drama, which captures the journey of an engineering graduate Abhishek, who for lack of a better job option joins as secretary of a panchayat office in a remote village of Uttar Pradesh.

name: NGK
description: Suriya plays the title role Nandha Gopalan Kumaran, who has completed M.Tech, Ph.D doing organic farming for his living and do social work without any returns, leaving the corporate job, living a happy life with his parents and wife Sai Pallavi. At one point of time, opposition party's Bala Singh induces the idea of joining him in politics and circumstances led him to join the party too.

name: The Hangover
description: When three friends gather for a weekend-long bachelor party in Vegas, they think they had a good time. But they are suffering the dreadful after-effects of girls, party and alcohol. And then they realize they have somehow lost the groom! Now, they must struggle to retrace their wild weekend to find their friend and deliver the bridegroom to his wedding — as they suffer from one killer Hangover!

name: Sardara And Sons
description: Sardara, his younger son and their wives relocate to Canada to live with his elder son, Daljeet and his wife. Cultural clashes force them to move out.

name: 13B: Fear Has a New Address
description: A man experiences a supernatural occurrence at his newly purchased apartment; a soap opera being telecast exclusively on his TV, which shows the future of his family.

name: Kuttram Kuttrame
description: An innocent family that hails from a village is struck by an unfortunate incident, which webs them into conflicts they never expected. Their smooth life is shattered and their world turns upside down. How the family deals with the labyrinth of conflicts is the rest of the movie.

name: Smurfs: The Lost Village
description: The Smurfs embark on a journey through the Forbidden Forest to find a mysterious village.

name: Project Wolf Hunting
description: During transport from the Philippines to South Korea, a group of dangerous criminals unites to stage a coordinated escape attempt. As the jailbreak escalates into a bloody, all-out riot, the fugitives and their allies from the outside exact a brutal terror campaign against the special agents onboard the ship.

name: Sherlock: Series 4
description: Benedict Cumberbatch and Martin Freeman reprise their iconic roles as Sherlock and Watson.

name: Maja Ma
description: Pallavi Patel is the quintessential, middle aged, devoted housewife who is equally famous for her dance as she is for her cooking. But what happens when a rumor about her, threatens to disrupt her middle-class family’s ethos, on the eve of her son Tejas’ engagement with a rich, NRI girl?

name: Phir Ek Maidan E Jung
description: When a vengeful man with criminal ties starts hunting down his family, Dr. Mikhael vows to protect them and annihilate his enemy.

name: ERUMBHU
description: Muthu has a tiny wish, but that wish puts Muthu and Pachaiammaa in crisis. They must find a solution to this problem within a month without their grandmother, father, and stepmother knowing it.

name: Fleabag Season 1
description: Fleabag is a hilarious and poignant window into the mind of a dry-witted, sexual, angry, grief-riddled woman, as she hurls herself at modern living in London. Award-winning playwright Phoebe Waller-Bridge writes and stars as Fleabag, an unfiltered woman trying to heal, while rejecting anyone who tries to help her and keeping up her bravado all along.

name: King of Thieves
description: A true crime movie about a crew of retired crooks who pull off a major heist in London's jewelry district. What starts off as their last criminal hurrah, quickly turns into a brutal nightmare due to greed.

name: Sharkwater Extinction
description: Sharkwater Extinction is a thrilling, action adventure journey that follows filmmaker Rob Stewart as he exposes the billion dollar illegal shark fin industry and the political corruption behind it.

name: Hunt
description: ACP Arjun Prasad has managed to track down his friend's killer when he meets with an accident resulting in partial memory loss. Soon, he is reassigned to investigate the murder and find the culprit.

name: Blumhouse's Truth Or Dare (Unrated Director's Cut)
description: In this intense Unrated Director's Cut, a game of "Truth or Dare" among friends turns deadly when someone-or something-begins to punish those who tell a lie or refuse the dare.

name: Meet Cute
description: When Sheila and Gary meet, it’s love at first sight - until we realize their magical date wasn’t fate at all. Sheila’s got a time machine, and they've been falling in love over and over again. But when the perfect night is never quite enough, Sheila travels to Gary’s past to change him into the perfect man.

name: The Twilight Saga: Eclipse (Hindi)
description: In this Hollywood / English dubbed movie, the third film in the TWILIGHT franchise. Torn between Edward and Jacob, Bella must also confront a vengeful vampire and a string of grisly murders that terrorize Seattle.

name: E.T. the Extra-Terrestrial
description: Relive the adventure and magic in one of the most beloved motion pictures of all-time, E.T. The Extra-Terrestrial, from Academy Award®-winning director Steven Spielberg. Captivating audiences of all ages, this timeless story follows the unforgettable journey of a lost alien and the 10-year-old boy he befriends.

name: Mahanati (Hindi)
description: Savitri, the most admired actress from South Indian cinema, goes through various tragic incidents in her personal life. Unable to cope with depression, she eventually becomes an alcoholic.

name: DANGEROUS
description: Set on leaving his violent, deadly past behind, a dangerous sociopath heads to a remote island to investigate the mystery behind his brother's demise, but when a deadly gang of mercenaries arrives ashore, he must put aside his new code of ethics in order to save his family - at all cost.

name: VIVARIUM
description: A Young couple thinking about buying their perfect single family starter home. They visits a real estate agency where they are received by a strange sales agent and find themselves trapped in a surreal, mysterious, maze-like nightmare.

name: Border
description: Border Is A Bollywood Epic War Hindi Action Movie, Directed By J. P. Dutta, Starring Sunny Deol, Sunil Shetty, Akshaye Khanna, Jackie Shroff, Sudesh Berry, Puneet Issar And Kulbhushan Kharbanda In The Lead Roles. A Band Of 120 Indian Soldiers In Longewala Region Defend Their Post All Night Until They Receive Assistance From The Indian Air Force The Next Morning.

name: Drishyam 2 (Hindi)
description: Seven years after the case related to Vijay and his family was closed, a series of unexpected events brings a truth to light that threatens to change everything for the Salgaonkars.

name: Venom
description: Venom is a fright-filled voodoo thriller set deep in the eerie swamps of southern Louisiana. When a group of teenagers try to uncover the truth behind a friend's mysterious death, they encounter an evil force more deadly than anyone could imagine.

name: Pagalpanti
description: 3 men, considered as losers in their lives by the people, plan to get rich along with their girlfriends by fooling 2 gangsters and robbing their money.

name: Veerappan
description: A police official assembles an elaborate network of spies and undercover operatives to bring down a ruthless bandit with a private army.

name: DOLLU
description: Dollu is about Bhadra, a Dollu drummer-dancer who is struggling to regroup his Dollu Kunitha team to keep the age-old traditions alive. What happens when urbanization affects this small village in Karnataka and its indigenous artform; forms the story of Dollu.

name: W: Two Worlds Apart (Hindi) - Season 1
description: After being pulled into the webtoon world created by her father, a surgical resident gets entangled in a murder mystery involving the story's hero.

name: Tiger Zinda Hai
description: The action drama Tiger Zinda Hai is a sequel to the blockbuster Ek Tha Tiger. When a group of Indian & Pakistani nurses are held hostage in Iraq by the militant Abu Usman, Indian Intelligence (RAW) tracks down the reclusive agent Tiger 8 years after he fled with former Pakistani Intelligence (ISI) agent Zoya. Joining the forces for humanity, Tiger & Zoya set out on a rescue mission.

name: Battleship
description: From Hasbro the company that brought you Transformers, Battleship is an epic-scaled action adventure that unfolds across the seas, in the skies and over land as our planet fights for survival against a superior alien force.  Battleship features some of the most incredible special effects and breathtakingly explosive action sequences ever filmed!

name: Tashan
description: A cool call center executive Jimmy Cliff (Saif Ali Khan), a wannabe gangster Bachchan Pande (Akshay Kumar), a beautiful girl Pooja (Kareena Kapoor) who can't be trusted, Bhaiyyaji (Anil Kapoor) a gangster who enjoys killing people as much as he enjoys learning to speak English come together on a journey across India. A journey which will alter the course of their lives in more ways than one.

name: Upload - Season 3
description: Prime Video’s #1 comedy is back! In Season 3, the recently downloaded Nathan and Nora start an IRL relationship while taking down Freeyond. Meanwhile, a digital copy of Nathan is brought to life in Lakeview where he explores an alternate path with Ingrid. Aleesha is promoted to manager and has a new workplace love interest, and a lonely Luke looks for work in the Grey Zone.

name: Arranged
description: What happens when an arranged marriage between Tarun and Richa meanders into discovering truths about each other on their very first date.

name: Everything is fine
description: Everything is fine is a powerful short by #MansiNiraJain that will make you pause and ask your mother, "How are you?” and truly listen to her reply like you have never listened before.

name: Ghazi (Telugu)
description: Inspired by true events, The Ghazi Attack is India's first underwater war film. The story revolves around the events that unfolded right before the Indo-Pakistan war of 1971, when the Pakistani Submarine Ghazi (Asia's most powerful fast-attack submarine at the time) attempted to destroy the Indian aircraft carrier Vikrant.

name: Rebel
description: After His Parents Are Brutally Murdered, Rishi Sets Out On A Quest To Find The Killers. He Finds That His Own Uncle, Who Has Now Disguised Himself As Robert, Is Involved In The Killings.

name: Freaky Ali
description: After a chance encounter with a golfer inspires him, Ali, a debt collector working for a gangster, pursues the sport professionally. Soon, he becomes a champion, but he must face a corrupt rival.

name: Shakuntala Devi
description: The extraordinary story of Shakuntala Devi, the world-renowned mathematician who lived her life on her own terms. While the film pays tribute to her genius as a mathematician, it also humanizes her as a woman and mother, in trying to capture her indomitable spirit. Told through the lens of her relationship with her daughter Anu, the film highlights their very different struggles and aspirations.

name: Sesh Anka
description: A murder A convict A honest headstrong Cop And then steps in an old horse who is too good at the game! Now wait for 'The Last Act"

name: Bleeding Steel
description: A Special Forces Agent is assigned to protect a scientist and his creation from a sinister gang.

name: Good Morning
description: Anagha's day starts, more or less, like millions of other working women. Even though she obviously has a hi-profile professional job, Anagha is hands-on with her family matters. It is only when Anagha gets to her workplace, that the nature of her job is revealed - providing the twist in the tale.
